Mamin Jehová, a a kꞌanej cꞌam chi qꞌuexchaji; aycꞌal ecꞌ yin tojbalkꞌinal bay satcan.
A in mimanil chi bilaj a satak, yujtol chin xiw bay a ley.
Axa pax ach Mamin, cawil ayach ecꞌok, yel ton chi yal masanil a chekbanil.
Najatilxa wecꞌ cajan xol eb cꞌam chi yochej juncꞌulal.
Axca yayji oc witzlak yinlak Jerusalén, caywal tuꞌ yayji oc Jehová yinlak is conob tinaniꞌ, cꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal.
Atacꞌal yich olan ayin ecꞌok, cax chi walon in ba ayach, Mamin Jehová.
Ex chekbej Jehová, jalek watxꞌ kꞌanej bay. Alek watxꞌ kꞌanej bay Cham, mac ex ayex ecꞌ yul is templo yet akꞌbalil.
A Cham max watxꞌnen cꞌu cꞌal xajaw, yujtol aycꞌal is camcꞌulal Cham yin tojbalkꞌinal.
Max in a takꞌwej, yet max ach wawteni, cax max aj can aon oc wip.
cꞌal yul kꞌab eb chi nacꞌal yobtakil; asan owal chi na eb masanil tiempo.
Manxa animaok ay in cꞌul tinaniꞌ, sombinak ay in cꞌul.
Ach Jehová, watxꞌ ton wal a cꞌul, cax ay a yabencꞌulal, miman a cꞌul Mamin, cax chi okꞌ a cꞌul jin.
Yelxacꞌal ton miman yayji co Diosal tiꞌ, miman is yipalil, cax cꞌam lajubal is jelanil.
A Cham max akꞌon jun co Reyal miman yipalil.
Tekan ok yal eb ayach axca tiꞌ: Ocan jetok, yet watxꞌ chon makwaj yulak be yet chi co makꞌon cam junok anima chi ecꞌ bay tuꞌ, caxcꞌal cꞌam is mul ayon.
Axca tuꞌ ok yun yayji ecꞌ jelanilal yin a nabal, cax ok akꞌon a nabal yetok tzet yetal ojtak tuꞌ.
Yetok is jelanilal, cꞌal ojtakbilal max watxꞌnej Jehová satcan, cꞌal sat txꞌotxꞌ tiꞌ.
Manchak ach oc xol eb, akꞌcꞌal ep a toj a satak.
Watxꞌokab cꞌal yili ix yul a sat, axca wal junok noꞌ txꞌucchej; cꞌam chi lajwi a tzalojcꞌulal yin, ayokabcꞌal a tzalojcꞌulal yuj is camcꞌulal ix.
Tatol ay mac chi yochej chi yitok kꞌakꞌej txam is cꞌul, chi tzꞌatok is pichil yuj.
Yuj tu xin ach in cꞌajol, ab wal tzet ok walaꞌ. Taynej ab in kꞌanej tiꞌ.
A yet max watxꞌnen Cham asun bay satcan, cax max tenon oc waan nukꞌlak aꞌ mar,
A yuj isajil, xan ok ach oc mebail. Ta yelcꞌulal chach mulnaj xin, ok ach oc beyomal.
A mactxel tojol is nabal, a ton is tojolal tuꞌ chi ikbani; a pax mac etnewom xin, chi lajwi ay yuj is yetnewomalil tuꞌ.
A eb a yobtakilal ayoc yipok cꞌul, lajan eb axca junok na watxꞌnebil yiban arena; a pax eb watxꞌ is nabal xin, tecꞌan waay eb axca junok tzet yetal caw is xeꞌ.
A is tojolal junok anima, a cꞌam chi chaon low yin; a pax yobtakilal xin, a chi akꞌon low yin eb yobtakwom.
Ay wal be tol watxꞌ jaloni; ti tol a pax bay camich chon yicantok.
Cꞌam chi cha cꞌul Jehová is xajanbal eb yobtakwom, a pax eb watxꞌ is nabal xin, watxꞌ chi yun chalay is txaj eb.
Yuj watxꞌcꞌulal, cꞌal ikemal, xan chi akꞌlay tan yobtakilal; tatol ay yelapnok Jehová yul co sat, chon el xol yobtakilal.
A mac yobtakwom, chi cha yab yobal kꞌanej, a mac lekꞌtiꞌ, chi cha yab wajoj kꞌanej.
A yuj is kꞌanej junok yob nabal xan chi lowcan yin; yuj is kꞌanej tuꞌ xan chi oc txꞌan lasu yin is nukꞌ yet chi sutꞌlay camok.
Chi chalay na cꞌal beyomal yin satakejal bay eb mamej; a pax ix etbiej aj nabal, chi chalay bay Jehová.
Ta ay mactxel chi wabaj ba yin junok txꞌok animail, checan el is pichil, cax cheoncan yin majanbilal.
A mactxel chi yaxacꞌal oc ba yul kꞌab ochewalil yin uqꞌuej an, cꞌal yin mimek loj, yinxacꞌal mebail chi yuncanok.
Ab xin, ok ach in cuy yin tzet yetal max yal eb aj nabal, chi cam a cuyon xin.
Manchak a junanej a ba yetok eb uqꞌuem an, tamwal yetok eb yelxacꞌal chi ecꞌ yiban lowi,
Manchak ach tzaloj yet chi aycꞌay mactxel ajcꞌul oc en.
A wal junok chekbej yikem, lajan wal bay is patrón axca yet chi juqꞌuen siquilaꞌ yet ay co takintial xol kꞌakꞌ, chi sicbi cꞌul cham yet chi chekoni.
A junok isaj chi na tol jelan yintak ukwanok anima yojtak chi takꞌwi yin watxꞌil.
Axca chi yun jilon aytok co sat yul junok aej, cay cꞌapax tuꞌ chi yun jion co nabal yet chi jilon oc is nabal junok jet animail.
A yet ok beycꞌaltok tiempo, miman yelapnok eb max on tenchaneni, yintak pax eb max tzꞌak yal watxꞌ kꞌanej jin.
Xiwil mactxel chi sayon is watxꞌcꞌulalil eb yajaw; palta asan Jehová chi watxꞌnen el kꞌanej yin watxꞌil.
a no coj, a noꞌ tuꞌ yelxacꞌal ay is may noꞌ, tol cꞌam chi elaj noꞌ bay satak junok mactxel;
A eb yuneꞌ, cꞌal yichamil, chi yal eb watxꞌ kꞌanej yin, cax chi yalon eb axca tiꞌ:
Lajwi tuꞌ, max wilon oc masanil in mulnajil max in watxꞌnej tiꞌ, a ton juntzan mulnajil tol yatakil max yun watxꞌji wuj, caytuꞌ max yun nachaj el wuj tol a masanil juntzan tuꞌ, cꞌam wal jabok yelapnok. Lajanxacꞌal axca jakꞌon jip co mitxꞌon cakꞌekꞌ, cꞌam junok tzet yetal tol watxꞌ chi jiꞌ bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ.
Cax max wilon cꞌapaxok, tol a bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, a yet chi beycꞌulnelay eb anima, bay is moj wal tol ay watxꞌil, cꞌal tojolal, palta asan tzet yetal man watxꞌok chi uji.
A mactxel tol ay is camcꞌulal yin chꞌen tumin, tol chi ajcꞌal can yocheni. A mactxel ay is camcꞌulal yin beyomal, cꞌam yechel tol ok naꞌ tol kꞌokbilxa tzet yetal ay bay. Nabacꞌal chi yetnej eb cꞌul.
Yelxacꞌal watxꞌ yet chi lajwi ay junok tzet yetal, yintak yet chi chalay el yich.
Masanil juntzan tiꞌ max wilaꞌ, yet max in oc ijan wojtaknen el tzet yetal chi uj bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, a bay ay anima tol ay yikbej ayocok, chi yakꞌbalnej yikbej tuꞌ yin yetnen yet animail.
Ta a junok yajaw chi tit yowal en, manchak a kꞌanil a ba yin opiso bay ayach ocok. Ta che ay a ba, chi jeꞌ watxꞌji ay a faltail, caxcꞌal miman yayji ocok.
Axa ok yunej, a e kꞌab chex colon tinaniꞌ, toxacꞌal ok bilok, a e yakan tol tecꞌan waayi ok pax yip. Cꞌamxa cꞌapax e ye yin e cachꞌon e lobej, manxa ok low cꞌapax e sat yin watxꞌ.
Lajan in axca junok an xumac bay jobeal yet Sarón, axca an chochol chi chꞌib bay acꞌal, ẍi ix.
A wal a nukꞌ, lajan wal axca torre watxꞌnebil yuj David, ayoc 1,000 makbal julbalej yet eb soldado jelan yelbubok.
A nak in camcꞌulnebil tuꞌ, mayal toj nak bay yawoj, bay awbil yawoj tol sumumixacꞌal yel jabil; max toj nak yakꞌ tzalojbok cꞌul, cꞌal wajon is xumac.
¿Mactxel jun ix chi tit bay tzꞌinan txꞌotxꞌ, tol pakan ay bay yiban jolom xicꞌ is camcꞌulnebil? ẍi eb.
Ex in conob ¿tzet yuj xan max occan conob Jerusalén axca junok ajmul ix? A yet yalantok a tojolal chi beybalnej eb, axa wal tinaniꞌ makꞌom cam anima eb.
Axa yet ok aj wan Jehová ul yakꞌon bil txꞌotxꞌ txꞌotxꞌ tiꞌ, ok octok eb anima yulak jatilal nachꞌenlak, cꞌal yulak jatilal chꞌen mimek chꞌen, yuj xiwilal bay Cham tol ay is may, tol miman yikbej.
A yet ok yakꞌon Cham Yajaw lowbanilej cax ok yaon oc yailal, ok yican el chicꞌ ayoc yin kꞌab eb aj Jerusalén yuj is makꞌon cam animail eb, cax ok sakbanej eb aj Sión yin is yobtakil.
A yul nukꞌ eb, axca wal yet no coj, ok el yaw eb axca wal tzꞌibcoj tol chi mocꞌ aj is chibej; watxꞌ wal ok yun yiontok, cax cꞌam mactxel ok jeꞌ tokꞌon ecꞌ bay.
Axa Jehová Cham Jajawil chi alon axca tiꞌ: Cꞌam bakꞌin ok yuncan el jun nabal eb nak tuꞌ.
Ayin Jehová Yajaw in yin Masanil, a yul a sat Asanxanej inokab Ocok. A ayin moj chach xiwi. Watxꞌ tatol ay welapnok yul a sat.
Okꞌbal ex cꞌul ayex che watxꞌnej juntzan ley man tojolok tiꞌ, tol chi etax eb anima yuj.
A tinaniꞌ chi oc wanaj eb soldado tuꞌ bay Nob. Chi txꞌox eb yowal cꞌul yin tzalan Sión bay conob Jerusalén.
Yuj tu xin, a masanil anima ok pax yip yuj xiwcꞌulal.
Palta xin, wal yel, mayal ach aytok bay makbej camich, atacꞌal bay najatil yich xab olan max ach ayapnok.
axa jun yinatil David ok oc yin reyalil, ok yakꞌ yajawilal xol anima yetok camcꞌulal, cꞌal yin baycꞌal ijanilal. Ayman ok watxꞌnej tojolal, cax ok yiloni tol tojolcꞌal ok yun eb juez.
A yet tuꞌ, ok ilaytek ofrenda bay Jehová Cham Yajaw yin Masanil, yuj jun conobal anima mimek is tel, tol cꞌam xil is mimanil eb, a ton jun nación ay is may binaj bay masanil conob, caw wal tecꞌan eb, tol chi aycꞌay nacionlak yuj, cajan bay jun txꞌotxꞌ tol pojquiltak yuj mimek aej. A yofrenda eb tuꞌ, ok yitek eb bay tzalan Sión, bay chi oc ayilal bay Jehová Cham Yajaw yin Masanil.
A wal eb anima max yaoc Egipto, cꞌal Etiopía yipok is cꞌul, ok xiwcan aj eb, cꞌal qꞌuixwi aj eb yuj tzet ok utlay cab conob tuꞌ.
A tiꞌ e yet, asan tzalojcꞌulal che yun yin e kꞌin. Che yakꞌ cam no wacax cꞌal no calnel, chi oc loj cꞌal uqꞌuej vino e yuj. Che yaloni: Lowokonek, juqꞌuek an, yujtol talaj a yet yecal chon cami, quex chi.
A jantak ok yiꞌ eb tuꞌ, yet Jehová ok yunej. Cꞌamcꞌal tzet ok cꞌuaytok, palta tol ok akꞌlay bay eb chi akꞌon serbil Cham, yet watxꞌ chi man eb mimanok is lobej, cꞌal manon eb pichilej watxꞌ.
A bay jun tzalan tiꞌ ok yiel Jehová cuscꞌulal ayoc yiban masanil nación, axca junok kꞌapej bacꞌan oc yin junok anima.
Cꞌamtek wowal yin. Matawal ay qꞌuix, ma yobal acꞌun ayaj in satak, chi mi in tecꞌayok, chi wakꞌon tzꞌa yin junelnej.
Axca max yut mulnaj ba Jehová bay witz Perazim, cꞌal bay yacꞌalil yul yet Gabaón, caytuꞌ ok yut mulnaj ba yin tzet chi yochej cꞌul, tol cꞌayubtakxacꞌal ok yunej.
A mactxel tol ayoc yin somcꞌulal, ok cuychaj el jelanilal yuj, a eb chi alxi ajok, ok cha yab eb cuybanilej, ẍi Jehová.
A wal eb aj Asiria, ok xiwcan aj eb yet ok yaben eb yul nukꞌ Jehová cax ok makꞌlay kꞌaj eb yuj Cham yetok is kꞌokoch.
Watxꞌ e yet mac ex chex awwi bay tilak aꞌ aejlak, cax colan bay chi low e wacax, cꞌal e burro.
A toni, a wal yet jun cꞌual tuꞌ, ok yakꞌ Jehová paktzebal, a ton wal yet jun abil tuꞌ ok yican el Cham yowal cꞌul yuj tzet max utlay conob Sión yuj eb.
Axa takꞌwi Eliaquim tuꞌ, cꞌal Sebna, cꞌal Joa bay jun comandante tuꞌ axca tiꞌ:
Taynej wal ab xin Mamin, cha abej. Ila wal juntzan kꞌanej max tzꞌibejtek Senaquerib tiꞌ ayin. Masanil juntzan yobal kꞌanej tiꞌ chi yal en, ach Dios tol iquis achcꞌal.
Ok ach in col yetok conob Jerusalén tiꞌ yul kꞌab reyal Asiria. Ayin wal ok in colcꞌal jun conob tiꞌ, ẍi Jehová, cachi.
Max yalon cham Isaías bay cham rey Ezequías axca tiꞌ:
Ajanektek tꞌanan satcan tiꞌ: ¿Mactxel max esnen aj masanil juntzan tiꞌ? ẍi Cham. A Jehová max watxꞌneni, aꞌ chi ion eltek, cax chi bison waycan tuꞌ, cax yin is bi junjun chi yawten eltek. Yujtol miman yayji oc is yipalil Cham, cꞌam junok chi cꞌayaj yul kꞌab.
¿Mactxel max alon el yabixal jun tiꞌ tax yet yichbanil, yet watxꞌ chi jab yabixal on? ¿Mactxel max alon yin ayoktocꞌal yet payxa tuꞌ, yet watxꞌ chi jalaꞌ tol yel chi yalaꞌ? Tokwal ay junok ex yechelej ex tiꞌ max e yal tzet ok uj yet yajtok tuꞌ, tokwal ay anima max aben e yaloni.
Tol ayin Jehová in, e Colomal wayji, ayin ton Cham e Diosal tol Asanxanej in Ocok, ayin ok wakꞌbalnej Egipto, Etiopía cꞌal Sabá e manbanilok.
A Jehová Cham Rey chi akꞌon bekchaj el Israel. A ton Jehová, Cham Yajaw yin Masanil chi alon axca tiꞌ: Ayincꞌaltaꞌ ecꞌ yettax yichbanil, acꞌalaꞌ ayincꞌal ecꞌ yet lajubal, asannej in Dios in, cax cꞌam junokxa.
Okꞌbal wal cꞌul mactxel chi yakꞌ owal yetok Cham is watxꞌnemal. A jun cambejal anima tuꞌ, lajan wal yayji axca tzꞌakbejal txꞌotxꞌ cꞌun poji. Tokwal chi yal txꞌotxꞌ tzꞌakbejal txꞌotxꞌ bay mac chi tzꞌakon tuꞌ axca tiꞌ: ¿Tzet yetal chonej? Ach tiꞌ man ojtakok chach mulnaji, man ẍiok.
Ocokab yin chꞌen molino, cax beokab ixim trigo, yiokab el makil sat, jitzokab aj is pichil yin xub cax taxokab aꞌ aej.
Matawal max e yikej in chekbanil, axca wal mi aꞌ mimek aej cꞌam chi tani, caytuꞌ yayji e juncꞌulal tinaniꞌ, axca mi wal yajcꞌal pomnaj sat aꞌ mar, cay mi wal tuꞌ yayji e tojolal.
Ayin ok wakꞌ yunej tol ok makꞌlej cam ba eb chex etneni, axcaxacꞌal uqꞌuem an ok yun eb yuj is chichoncꞌulal, axca tol ok yucꞌlej eb is chiqꞌuil. Yuj tu xin, masanil anima ok ojtaknen elok tol ayin ton Jehová e Colomal in, ayin chex wakꞌ bekchajok. Ayin ton is Diosal in Jacob, tol chi jeꞌ wuj masanil, ẍi Jehová.
Mayal pax yip eb e yuninal, mayal aycꞌay eb axca no txꞌucchej chi can yul txꞌan yal, toxacꞌal max cancan teljab eb bay txiquinlak calle. Yastakxacꞌal eb yuj yowal cꞌul Jehová, yuj is yakꞌbal cuenta Cham.
Axca tiꞌ yalon Jehová: A Jerusalén, lajan wal axca junok ix ix tol cꞌamcꞌaltaꞌ yuneꞌ, bekbilcan yuj yichamil. Axa tinaniꞌ, moj tol chi awji, chi bitni yin tzalojcꞌulal, yujtol xiwilxa yuneꞌ ok yilaꞌ, yintak junok ix ix cꞌamcꞌal bay max beklaycan yuj yichamil.
Ta a junok txꞌok conobal chi yaoc ba yul in kꞌab, cꞌam jabok tzet chi yal axca tiꞌ: A wal Jehová cꞌam chin is chaoc yin ayilal xol is conob, man ẍiok. Cꞌam cꞌapax chi jeꞌ yalon eb winak ibil el yetbeyom is winakil axca tiꞌ: Ayin tiꞌ lajan in axca junok takin teꞌ, man ẍiok.
Max yalon Jehová ayin axca tiꞌ: Awjan yetok masanil ep, cꞌam chi aytek yul a nukꞌ, che wal aj can yul a nukꞌ, axca wal yokꞌ junok trompeta. Akꞌ yojtaknej el in conob, a ton eb yinatil Jacob, is tenomtakilal.
A ok paktzen bay junjun, atacꞌalaꞌ is yunben; ok ya wal oc yailal eb ajcꞌul oc yin. A bay mac chi chichon oc cꞌul yin, ok paktzej wal bay axca wal is mojalil, mawal eb conoblak cajan bay junxa kꞌaxepal aꞌ mar.
Ayex tiꞌ, tzꞌakanxacꞌal max yun e yaben yail qꞌuixwilal cꞌal e buchlayi; palta axa tinaniꞌ xin, tzꞌakan ok yun e chaon beyomal bay yin e txꞌotxꞌ, cꞌamxa lajubal e tzalojcꞌulal.
Max yion ecꞌtok is conob bay nan xol aꞌ aej. Majcꞌal telcꞌoj eb axcaxacꞌal yecꞌ no chej bay acꞌal,
Yuj wal tuꞌ, a eb in chekbej ay is lobej eb, axa ayex tiꞌ ok ex cam yuj wajil. Ay tzet ok yucꞌ eb, palta ayex tiꞌ ok ex cam yuj takintial. Tol ok tzalojbok eb, palta ayex tiꞌ qꞌuixawtakxacꞌal ok e yuncantok.
Yujtol wojtakxa is nabal eb, cꞌal is beybal eb, xan ok in jayoc ul in wajban oc masanil conoblak, cꞌal tiejlak yin in beycꞌulneni, axa jayoc eb ul yilon in maykꞌakꞌal tuꞌ.
Asiꞌ, cax chalon el bay eb aj conob Jerusalén yet chi yab eb: Axca tiꞌ yalon Jehová: Chin nawaltek e yikemal yet max ex wion oc in conobok. Caw wal ay e camcꞌulal win, axca junok kꞌopoj tolto max nupayi, caw wal ay is camcꞌulal yin yichamil. Max ex occꞌal tzakan wintak bay takin txꞌotxꞌ, bay jun makan txꞌotxꞌ tol cꞌam junok mac chi mulnaj bay.
Axca eb ix ajmul ix yojtak eb beal bay chi toj eb sayicꞌ winak, cay ex wal tuꞌ. Meẍtol ex yin yobtakil.
Ocokonek yin yaynakilal yuj qꞌuixwilal, yujtol ayon tiꞌ, yetok eb jichmam, caw wal yobtakwom oncꞌal bay Jehová co Diosal. Yettaxcꞌal unin onto, caw wal cꞌam on chi jikej bay Cham, ẍi eb.
A Jerusalén tol mayal etaxtok, lajanxa chi yut ba axca junok ix ix tol nabaxacꞌal chi pich ba yetok an púrpura, cax chi yaoc chꞌen oro manxa watxꞌilok yili yin, cax kꞌekxacꞌal chi yut bonon yinlak bakꞌ sat. Cꞌamxa jabok yelapnok yuj watxꞌnen aj ba tuꞌ, yujtol a eb winak ochebil yuj ix tuꞌ, mayal yajlaycan el ix yuj eb nak. Asan chi na eb nak tzet ok yun yakꞌon camok. Caytuꞌ yayji Jerusalén yetok juntzanxa nación.
Caw wal chi cꞌay co cꞌul yuj yobtakilal tzet chi uj bay jun nación tiꞌ.
Masanil eb caw wal yob is beybal. Anima tol cꞌamxa is nabal, alom kꞌumal eb. Max cawbi el eb. Lajanxacꞌal eb axca chꞌen bronce ma chꞌen hierro.
¡Ex aj Jerusalén, tzukek el xil e jolom yuj cuscꞌulal, cax che kꞌokon elok! A bay tzalanlak bay mayayi chi toj e bitnej bit yet cuscꞌulal, yujtol mayal ex in bekcan yuj yowal in cꞌul, ẍi Jehová.
Caw wal jelan eb yin yalon lekꞌtial kꞌanej. Asan yuj lekꞌtial kꞌanej chi aj can eb. Cꞌamxa kꞌanej yel chi al-layi. Yuj tuꞌ xan chi yal Jehová, tol asanxanej yobtakilal chi yun eb. Cꞌamxa chi yal cꞌul eb chi yaloc Cham eb is Diosalok.
¿Tok ay mactxel man mojok chi xiw ayach, tol reyal ach masanil nacionlak? Moj wal tol miman elapnok yul sat masanil anima. Xol eb jelan, cꞌal eb rey bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, cꞌam junokxa mactxel lajan etok.
Catatuꞌ a eb aj Judá, cꞌal eb cajyom bay Jerusalén, ok tok eb kꞌan colwal is diosal bay chi yakꞌ tzꞌa eb incienso tuꞌ; palta man ok jeꞌ yuj juntzan tuꞌ colon el eb bay jun yailal ok jay tuꞌ.
Lajwi tuꞌ max yalon pax Cham ayin junelxa:
¡Mamin Jehová! caxcꞌal miman txequel yayji co mul, palta colwajan jin on yet watxꞌ cꞌam chach al-lay yobal. Xiwil el pit on ayach, cax chi oc co yobtakil ayach.
