Asannej in wal ayin ecꞌ in txꞌoklil cax max wilon jun tuꞌ, caw wal max pax in chiqꞌuil, cꞌamxa wip max wabej.
A jun ok jeꞌ yuj tuꞌ, ok yunxacꞌal tzet chi cha cꞌul yin jun ok aycꞌay yuj tuꞌ. Cꞌamxa mactxel ok jeꞌ tecꞌban ba satak. Ok oc bay txꞌotxꞌ yelxacꞌal watxꞌ, a ton Israel, cax ok yakꞌon cꞌayil jantakcꞌal ok yochej cꞌul.
Ay wal mimek yailal yet tuꞌ. Cꞌam junelok maxax yakꞌ axca tuꞌ yettaxcꞌal max el yich tzꞌunchaj nacionlak. A wal yet tuꞌ, masanil eb a conob ok colchajok, chi yal elapnok, a ton mactxel tzꞌibbil is bi bay yul txꞌan libro.
Palta maj yojtaknej elok, tatol ayin chi wakꞌ is trigo, is vino, cꞌal is yaceite; tol ayin chi wiaj can plata cꞌal oro chi yakꞌ bay Baal.
A yuj ajmulal, cꞌal yuj uqꞌuej an, xan sucxacꞌal chi yuncan el nabal eb.
A eb anima bay conob Galaad, caw wal yaxcꞌayinak eb, chicꞌxacꞌal chi ecꞌcan bay tuꞌ.
A conob Efraín, xiwil altar chi watxꞌnej ajok yuj yel is mul yaloni, palta yuj juntzan altar tuꞌ xan chi aj can yaon oc is mul.
A yet yalantok, lajan conob Efraín axca junok no wacax mayal aytek is tiꞌ, yikemxacꞌal tecꞌwi trigo; a tel is nukꞌ manxa watxꞌilok, majcꞌal waoc yugo yin. Palta a tinaniꞌ, ok waoc yugo yin, yet ok oc wal yin mulnajil. A eb aj Judá, a yetok arado ok mulnajok, axa pax juntzanxa eb yinatil Jacob xin, a yetok rastrillo ok mulnaj eb.
Palta a wal eb anima yet Efraín, max txꞌem wal eb yowal cꞌul Jehová. Caw wal max yakꞌ eb cabax el cꞌul Cham. Yuj wal tuꞌ ok yakꞌ Cham tojlanej el eb jantak yobtakilal max yun eb, acꞌal oc yuj is yobtakilal eb tuꞌ ok aycꞌay yiban.
Mayal oc jun miman bulan chapulín bay yul co txꞌotxꞌ, axca wal ejército. Caw wal cꞌamxa chi bischaji, yelxacꞌal ay is may. A ye noꞌ, lajan wal axca ye no coj.
Lajwi tu xin, ok txꞌox Jehová is camcꞌulal, cꞌal is yabencꞌulal ayon is conob on tiꞌ,
Axca wal bil cꞌu, caywal tuꞌ ok yun jakon Jehová yul is nukꞌ, tacꞌal bay jolom witz Sión bay Jerusalén. Axa satcan cꞌal txꞌotxꞌ txꞌotxꞌ ok bilajok. Axa Cham ok colon is conob, a ton conob Israel.
Axa ayex tiꞌ, max e yakꞌ pural eb wet-xa yayji yucꞌwi an, cax max e tenchanen eb in chekbej yin yalon el in kꞌanej.
Yuj wal tuꞌ xan axca tuꞌ ok ex wut ex aj Israel. Yujtol axca ton tuꞌ ok wunej, xan watxꞌnejek e ba, tol ok e yil-lej oc e sat wetok ayin e Diosal in tiꞌ, ẍi Jehová.
Ayex tiꞌ cꞌam che yochej che naꞌ, tol lanan jay jun cꞌual yailal. Palta a yuj tzet che yunej, xan lanan jayoc e cawilal.
Max yalon Amasías bay Amós axca tiꞌ:
A yet chi oc matxan Jehová Dios, Cham Yajaw yin Masanil, yin txꞌotxꞌ txꞌotxꞌ tiꞌ, chi uljitok txꞌotxꞌ, axa yokꞌaj masanil eb cajyom bay txꞌotxꞌ. Toxacꞌal chi ayi chi aj txꞌotxꞌ yuj yipal Cham, axca wal chi yut ba aꞌ miman aej Nilo.
A eb israel cajan bay txꞌotxꞌ Néguev, ok yiꞌ eb txꞌotxꞌ siquilal txꞌotxꞌ yul yet Esaú. Acꞌalaꞌ eb cajan bay pananlak, ok yiꞌ cꞌapax eb txꞌotxꞌ txꞌotxꞌ yet eb filisteo. Ok yion pax eb israel is txꞌotxꞌal Efraín, cꞌal txꞌotxꞌ is makbej Samaria junelxa. Axa eb yet Benjamín ok ioncan txꞌotxꞌ Galaad.
Max in mukaycantok yuj aꞌ aej. Max in toj wal bay najatilal yich aꞌ mar. Max oc bacꞌan juntzan acꞌun ay yulak aꞌ tuꞌ yin in jolom.
—Tokwal ach max aw te teꞌ tiꞌ, tamwal ach max akꞌ chꞌibok. Yet jun kꞌekbintakil max chꞌibi, axa yet junxa kꞌekbintakil max takilok. Palta ach ayxacꞌal a cuscꞌulal yuj teꞌ.
Catatuꞌ max waloni: Ex yajawil conob Israel, abek wal tinaniꞌ. ¿Tom man e mojok ayex tiꞌ e yojtaknen el tzet yetal tol tojol?
Lajan wal ok yun pax is conob Jacob tuꞌ nan xol xiwil nacionlak axca junok no coj ay xol no xolakilteal noꞌ, ma axca junok no coj chi oc xol junok bulan calnel. A yet chi oc noꞌ xol noꞌ tuꞌ, cax chi mitxꞌoni, chi cocꞌ tzilnentok. Cꞌamxa junok chi bekcan el yin yiquisal.
Ex tol ajcꞌul ex oc jin, manchak ex tzaloj yuj tzet chon oni. Caxcꞌal chon aycꞌayi, palta ok on aj pax wan junelxa. Caxcꞌal chi oymoj oc kꞌekkꞌinal jin, palta a Jehová ayoc co sakkꞌinalok.
Txꞌokxa toj is carruaje eb yulak calle, xuyuyixacꞌal yecꞌ yinlak txonbal; lajan wal yili axca junok tzektebalej tol ayoc is kꞌakꞌal, lajanxacꞌal yecꞌ eb axca rayo.
¿Tzet xan wal chakꞌ wil jantak yailal cꞌal yobtakil tiꞌ? Caw wal ay yaxcꞌayinakil cꞌal uchlejbail winlak. Masanilxacꞌal bay ay owal cꞌal teyelejbail.
Ach tiꞌ, max a kꞌakay te mimek teꞌ bay Líbano; axa tinaniꞌ, chach akꞌlay lajwok ayok, max a makꞌ cam no noꞌ bay tuꞌ, axa tinaniꞌ axa noꞌ ok aon oc xiwcꞌulal en. Caytuꞌ ok ach utlay yuj eb, yujtol xiwil mac max a makꞌ camok, cax cꞌam a yabencꞌulal yin anima bay yulyibankꞌinal, yetokcꞌal is conoblak.
A yet jun cꞌual tuꞌ, ok ablay yoc aw bay puertail yet no txay, bay yet is cab makan conob. Cax miman ok yun bil pojtok bay tzalanlak.
Yuj tu xin, echbanejek jayoc jun cꞌual yet ok in aj wan, yin in txꞌoxon el is yobtakil masanil eb yobtakwom. Ayin wal caw Jehová in chi walaꞌ: Mayal in naꞌ tol ok in wajbaj oc masanil nacionlak cꞌal makbejlak, yet ok wiel yowal in cꞌul yiban eb. Masanil yulyibankꞌinal ok lajwok ayok yuj kꞌakꞌal yowal in cꞌul.
Aycꞌal oc Wespíritu e yetok atacꞌalaꞌ max yun wakꞌon in tiꞌ yet max ex el bay Egipto, xan cꞌamcꞌal chex xiwi.
Yinxacꞌal aymanil max yal cham ángel tuꞌ, tol chi walil juntzan kꞌanej tiꞌ: A ton juntzan tiꞌ max yal Jehová, Cham Yajaw yin Masanil: Ay wal in miman camcꞌulal yin Jerusalén, cꞌal yin tzalan Sión.
Junej ay cab te olivo yetok jun batxlub candil tuꞌ, jun ayoc bay is watxꞌ, cꞌal junxa bay is qꞌuexan, quin chi bay.
Max lajwi tuꞌ, max awji jun ángel tuꞌ ayin axca tiꞌ: Ila wali, a yuj jun carruaje max toj bay nación bay norte, xan ok oc wanaj yowal cꞌul Jehová yiban nación tuꞌ, ẍi.
A ton jun tiꞌ chi yal Jehová Cham Yajaw yin Masanil: Tecꞌbajek e ba, ayex tol lanan e yaben juntzan kꞌanej maxax yalil eb in chekbej yettax max ay yich ca watxꞌnelay in templo, ayin Jehová Yajaw in yin Masanil.
Caw wal watxꞌ xin, caw wal watxꞌ yili eb aj conob tuꞌ. Yuj xiwil trigo cꞌal vino, watxꞌxacꞌal ok yun chꞌib eb achꞌej cꞌal eb kꞌopoj.
Ayin Jehová in tiꞌ, ok wut tol yuj Jerusalén ok ecꞌ kꞌekꞌon juntzan nacionlak ay is cawilal tuꞌ, axca uqꞌuem an, a yet ok yakꞌon eb owal yin Jerusalén tuꞌ, cꞌal yin juntzanxa conoblak ay yul yet Judá.
Ok cajay pax anima bay Jerusalén xin; cꞌamxacꞌal tzet ok na eb bay tuꞌ, yujtol manxa ok uchchajtok.
A wal yopiso eb sacerdote, tol chi cuylay eb anima yuj eb, yet chin yojtaknej el eb. Moj ton chi apni oc masanil anima bay eb, yet chi yaben eb cuybanilej, yujtol a eb tuꞌ, in chekbej yayji eb ayin Jehová in tol Yajaw in yin Masanil.
A yet jun cꞌual tuꞌ, ayex tiꞌ toxacꞌal ok e tecꞌtok eb yobtakwom, axca wal chi yun tecꞌlay ay tikꞌakꞌil tan, caytuꞌ ok e yut eb.
Max kꞌanlej eb:
Chi jakil eb is yobtakil bay Dios, cax chi akꞌlaycan bautizar eb yuj Juan bay yul aꞌ Jordán tuꞌ.
—Ach Satanás, elan in cꞌatan, yujtol chi yal yul txꞌan Un Tzꞌibbilcan axca tiꞌ: Iek ay e ba bay Cham Jajawil co Diosal. Asan Cham che yakꞌ serbil, ẍi txꞌan, ẍi Jesús bay.
A yet chi co tzekon co tzektebal, tokwal a yalan junok cajón chi jaoctok, palta a yiban serbil chi jajtok, yet watxꞌ chi tzektenelay masanil eb ayicꞌ yul na yuj.
Ta asan chꞌan eb chex camcꞌulneni ok e camcꞌulnej paxok, ¿xin ta ok e chaꞌ is paktzil jun e camcꞌulal tuꞌ che naꞌ? Toltax eb tekomel tojlabal, cayton tuꞌ chi beybalnej eb.
Yetok cꞌapaxok, ¿tzet xan chex oc il yuj e pichil? Iek e nabal yin an xumaquil acꞌun tinaniꞌ. A an xumac tuꞌ, cꞌam chi mulnaj an, tamwal chi txꞌalwi cꞌapax an.
Axa eb chi aben in kꞌanej, palta cꞌam chi yikej paxok, lajan eb axca junok winak cꞌam is nabal. A jun winak tuꞌ, a yiban pok max watxꞌnej yatut.
Axa yet max yilon Jesús tol manxa animaok oyanxacꞌal oc yin, max yikban ecꞌtok eb is cuywom bay junxa kꞌaxepal aꞌ mar.
Palta Jesús xin, max yojtaknej el tzet chi naoc eb yin, xan max yal bay eb axca tiꞌ:
Axa yet max apni oc Jesús bay yatut cham yajaw tu xin, max yiloni tol lanan xulay juntzan axca yili chirima, cax xiwil chi wekeki anima yokꞌi.
Chi ecꞌ e yalilok tol a Cham Yajaw bay satcan toxa ok txecloj wal is yikbej.
A eb asannej is cawil chi yaꞌilnej yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, ok cꞌayil is kꞌinal eb yin tojbalkꞌinal. Axa eb ok bek cꞌulok cam wuj xin, a ton eb tuꞌ ok cha kꞌinalej tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal.
Caytuꞌ max ot caytuꞌ Mamin, yujtol caytuꞌ max yun chaon a cꞌul, ẍi bay Dios.
Ay eb caw okꞌbal cꞌul, axca wal te pojil aj, ma xin axca junok mecha yet tzektebal toxa chi tani, caytuꞌ eb. Palta a ton ok colon el eb, man ok yakꞌ low yin eb. Cayton tuꞌ ok yunej, masantacꞌal ok occan yin Yajawilal. A yet ok yakꞌon Yajawilal tuꞌ, watxꞌ ok yutej.
Axa takꞌwi Cham bay axca tiꞌ:
Axa yet lanan wayi, chi jay mac ajcꞌul oc yin, cax chi ul tzicontok an awal an xol is trigo tuꞌ.
Ayex tiꞌ, cuybil exxa yin tzet chi yun yeloc eb anima chi oc yul kꞌab Cham aj satcan. Yuj tuꞌ xan chi jeꞌ e yakꞌon cuylay juntzan acꞌ cuybanilej yetok juntzan icham, ẍi bay eb.
Max low eb masanil xin, cax max nojcan cꞌul eb. Max lajwi tuꞌ max wajlay aj ixim bijquiltakil maxto cani, lajcawebto motx ixim max wajnaj ajok.
Cabsat ex. Yel ton taꞌ tzet albilcan yuj Isaías e yin yet max yalon axca tiꞌ:
Yuj tuꞌ xan max yal pax bay ix:
A yet max yalon Jesús axca tuꞌ bay eb, catatuꞌ max nachaj el yuj eb tol manak acaw yich pan chi yalaꞌ, palta tol a cuybanil eb fariseo cꞌal eb saduceo max yal Cham yichpanil.
Max jayoc Jesús cꞌatan eb, max matxban oc kꞌab yiban eb.
—Ta caytu xin, a eb uninalej man yowalilok chi yakꞌ eb yet.
A yet mayal beklay el nak tuꞌ, max ilchaj el junok yet mulnajwomal nak yuj. Ay mi jayebok quetzal jec bay nak. Yuj tuꞌ max oc mitxꞌnaj nak yin, cax max oc pitzꞌnaj nak yin nukꞌ jun winak tuꞌ. Max yalon nak bay: Itek chꞌen a majan tumin ayin wal tinaniꞌ, ẍi bay.
—¿Tzet yuj xan cha kꞌanlej ayin yuj tzet yetal watxꞌ? Jun chꞌan mactxel watxꞌ, asan Dios. Ta chochej cha chaꞌ jun kꞌinalej tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal tuꞌ, ikej chekbanil Dios, ẍi Cham bay.
Max yalon eb axca tiꞌ: A eb nak tzunanxa max jay mulnajil tiꞌ, junxanej hora max mulnaj eb nak; palta lajan pax tojol eb nak max yiꞌ jetok on, ayon max techajcꞌal ecꞌ cꞌu juj tiꞌ xol kꞌakꞌ, ẍi eb bay.
A yet lananxa yapni oc Jesús yetok eb is cuywom bay cawilal Jerusalén, max apni oc eb bay conob Betfagé, bay cawilal jun tzalan chi yik Olivo. Cax max chekon babjok Cham cawan eb is cuywom.
Wal yel chi wal ayex, tatol che yaoc Dios yin e cꞌul, cax cꞌam jabok che yakꞌ cabcꞌulal, tzancꞌal tzet ok jeꞌ e yuj. Man asannejok axca tzet max wut jun te tiꞌ ok jeꞌ e yuj. Palta caxcꞌal che yal yin jun witz tiꞌ: Elokab caytiꞌ, cax chi kꞌokonaytok ba yul aꞌ mar, ta quex chi, ok jeꞌ e yuj.
Yuj tuꞌ xan max yal pax Jesús bay eb axca tiꞌ:
—A ton yechel cham yajaw bay Roma, cꞌal is bi cham, ẍi eb.
A eb meẍtol yin ley Moisés yetok eb fariseo, ay ton yopiso eb cuywaj yin ley Moisés.
Abek. Ok in chektok juntzan eb chekbej Dios ayex, cꞌal juntzan eb jelan yin yet Dios, yetok juntzan eb meẍtol. Ay eb ok e yakꞌ camok, ok e curusnej eb. Ay eb, tol ok e makꞌ yulak nail bay che yakꞌ culto. Ok e yuktej ecꞌ eb bay conoblak.
Ta ay mac chi alon ayex axca tiꞌ: Ilek wali, tix Cham Cristo ayicꞌ caytiꞌ, ma: Ilek wali, tix ayicꞌ bay tuꞌ, ta ẍi e yutelayi, man e cha e yabej.
A eb cꞌam wal nabal tuꞌ, cꞌamxa yaceite eb max yitok, asancꞌal chꞌan jab ayay yul is candil eb tuꞌ.
Ayin rey in tiꞌ, ok wal bay eb ayicꞌ bay in watxꞌ kꞌab axca tiꞌ: Ayex tiꞌ, albilcan ayex yuj in Mam, tol ok yakꞌ is watxꞌcꞌulal ayex. Ocanek wetok bay ok wakꞌ yajawilal. Atax yet max watxꞌnen Dios yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, max watxꞌnencan jun tiꞌ e yuj.
—Ta chi waoc Jesús yul e kꞌab, ¿jantak chin e tojlanej? ẍi bay eb.
—Caxcꞌal mi ok in cam etok, palta tutun maj ach wiel win, ẍi Pedro tuꞌ bay. Acꞌalaꞌ yalon masanil eb cuywom tuꞌ.
Max bekcan eb cuywom tuꞌ Cham txꞌoklil, cax max toj eb elaj masanil.
Max naontek Pedro tzet max yal Jesús bay, yet max yalon axca tiꞌ: Oxelxa quin eon el en yin aloni tol mayin ojtakok, cax ok okꞌaj no caẍlan, ẍican Jesús bay. Yuj tuꞌ xan max eltok Pedro yina, max jichchaj cꞌul yokꞌ sicꞌlibil.
—A Barrabás chi jochej on cha bekilok, ẍi eb.
Chuman wal cꞌu, max kꞌekbi masanil yulyibankꞌinal, masantacꞌal yet a las tres.
Axa yalon jun ángel tuꞌ bay eb ix axca tiꞌ:
Max lajwi tu xin, max ilaytok Jesús yuj Yespíritu Dios bay tzꞌinan txꞌotxꞌ.
—Tonek bay juntzan aldea cawil-lak tiꞌ, tol ok tok walcan el kꞌanej Dios xolak anima, yujtol yuj jun tiꞌ, xan max quin jayi, ẍi bay eb.
A yet max yilon eb meẍtol yin ley Moisés cꞌal eb fariseo, tol max low Cham yetok eb yob beybal cꞌal eb tekom el tojlabal tuꞌ, max yalon eb bay eb is cuywom Cham axca tiꞌ:
Yujtol max yab eb kꞌumal tol xiwil milagro max yun Jesús, xan xiwil eb max jayoc bay. Ay eb aj Judea, cꞌal eb aj Jerusalén, yetok eb aj Idumea, cꞌal eb aj kꞌaxepaltok aꞌ Jordán. Ay cꞌapax eb max tit cawilal Tiro cꞌal Sidón.
Yujtol tzancꞌal mac chi iken axca wal chi yochej cꞌul Dios, a ton eb tuꞌ axca tol wuẍtak, axca tol wanab, axca tol in txutx, ẍi Jesús.
Axa yet chi takilok, cax chi polon ajok, yujtol chi ajapnok tiempoal yaji, ẍi Jesús.
—Legión in bi, yujtol xiwil co bey on, ẍi nak.
—Ach ix, max jaycan a cꞌul, yujtol max aoc a cꞌul win. Paxan yin tzalojcꞌulal. Ti mayal watxꞌji a cꞌul yin jun a yailal tiꞌ, ẍi bay ix.
Max yabaj cham rey Herodes juntzan tzet chi el yunen Jesús yet jun tiempoal tuꞌ, yujtol max pukil yabixal xol masanil anima, yuj tuꞌ, max yal axca tiꞌ:
Axa yoctok Jesús yul jun barco yetok eb is chekbej tuꞌ, max toj eb txꞌoklil bay cꞌam anima.
Ay juntzan eb fariseo, cꞌal juntzan eb meẍtol yin ley Moisés max tit bay Jerusalén, max wajbaj oc bulan ba eb yin Jesús.
A bay tuꞌ ay jun ix ix ay jun yuneꞌ ix unin, ayoc espíritu yob yin. Max yab ix txutxej tuꞌ kꞌumal, tol max apni oc Jesús bay tuꞌ, axa toj ix bay Cham, max bet ay jajan ix bay.
—¿Tzet yuj xan che kꞌan e yil junok milagro ayin? Wal yel chi wal ayex, cꞌam junok milagro ok txꞌoxlay e yilaꞌ, ẍi Cham.
—Ayin tiꞌ, Chekbilintek yuj Dios xol eb jet animail tiꞌ, palta yowalil xiwil yailal ok eqꞌuel wiban. A eb ichamtak winak ay yopiso, yetok eb yajawil sacerdote, cꞌal eb meẍtol yin ley Moisés, ok in yintaknej el eb. Ok in yakꞌ cam eb, palta a yet cabjial tuꞌ, ok in ictzoj ajok, ẍi bay eb.
—¿Tzet che teyelej e ba yin yetok eb? ẍi Cham bay eb.
Axa yiontek Jesús jun unin xol eb tuꞌ, max lacon ajok, axa yalon tuꞌ:
Max lajwi tuꞌ, max cꞌoli lacon aj Cham eb unin tuꞌ. Max yaon ajtok kꞌab yiban eb, cax max kꞌanon watxꞌcꞌulal Dios yiban eb.
—Yel toni, ok ex akꞌlay porobal axca ok yun wakꞌlay porobal. Axca yailal ok eqꞌuel wiban, caytuꞌ yailal ok eqꞌuel e yiban.
Max yiontek eb noꞌ bay Cham. Max yaon ajtok eb is pichil tzꞌamok noꞌ, axa yaj Jesús yiban noꞌ tuꞌ.
Axa cꞌoli yalubtanen eb is xol tuꞌ, cax max yalon eb axca tiꞌ: ¿Tzet wal chi jut jalon bay? Ta chi jalaꞌ tol a Dios akꞌnej yikbej, a xam yalon ayon tuꞌ: ¿Tzet yuj xan maj e yapax oc yin e cꞌul xin? ẍi mi.
—Mamin Meẍtol, a Moisés tzꞌibnejcan axca tiꞌ: Kꞌinalok ay junok mac chi cami, cax chi can yistzil, palta cꞌam junok yuninal max elcanok. Axa junok nak uẍtakejal yowalil chi ion ix, yet watxꞌ ta chi el yuninal junxa tuꞌ, axca tol yuninal nak max cam tuꞌ chi yun yoqui. Caytuꞌ max yut yaloncan Moisés.
Chotan ay Jesús yul templo junel, bay cawilal chabal ofrenda, max yiloncꞌal yaon aytok anima is yofrenda. Xiwil eb beyom mimantak chi yut yaon aytok yet.
Cax ok titcꞌay waycan satcan; yetokcꞌal juntzan tzet yetal ay is yipalil bay satcan, ok tzicobtanelayok.
—Asek bay conob. Ay jun winak ok e yil yin bay tuꞌ, ibil oc jun moc aej yuj. Chex tzaklojcꞌal yintak.
Max jitzontok ba janicꞌxa sataktok, cax max ay nojan sat txꞌotxꞌ. Max txajli yuj kꞌanoni, ta chi jeꞌ cꞌam chi jay jun yailal tuꞌ yiban.
Axa yaj wan cham sat sacerdote tuꞌ nan xol eb, max yalon bay Jesús axca tiꞌ:
—¿Tom cꞌam chach takꞌwi jabok? Ab wal jantak tzet chi yal eb en, ẍi bay.
—A… ach ton tiꞌ chochay templo Dios alaꞌ, cax cha watxꞌnen aj is qꞌuexel yin cabjial.
—Manchak ex xiwi. Ayex tiꞌ, a Jesús aj Nazaret che sayicꞌok, jun max alay oc yin curus. Mayal ictzoj ajok. Cꞌamxa mac ayicꞌ yul chꞌen tiꞌ. Ilekto wali bay max ul yacan octek eb tiꞌ.
A Juan tuꞌ ok babjok satak Cham Jajawil. Axca wal is nabal Elías, cꞌal is yikbej, caytuꞌ ok yun is nabal cꞌal is yikbej cꞌapaxok. Yuj tuꞌ xan ok yakꞌ chalej ba nabal eb mamej yetok eb uninalej. Aꞌ ok qꞌuexon cꞌapax nabal eb tenomtak yul sat Dios, yet watxꞌ chi watxꞌji oc beybal eb. Axca ton tuꞌ ok yut yakꞌon na ba cꞌul eb anima, cax ok qꞌuexon eb is nabal, yet watxꞌ ay eb watxꞌxa is nabal yet ok jay Cham Jajawil, ẍi jun ángel tuꞌ.
—Ach tiꞌ, yel miman watxꞌcꞌulal Dios max txꞌox ayach yintak masanil eb ix jet ixal. Miman cꞌapax watxꞌilal ok al-lay yin jun oneꞌ ok aljok tuꞌ.
Axca tuꞌ max yut yaloncan Dios, yet max yakꞌbalnen eb is chekbej yaloncan yet payxa, eb asan Dios aj cuenta yin.
Max lajwi tuꞌ, axa pax eb waynem calnel tuꞌ. Max yalon eb is watxꞌ kꞌanej bay Dios. Max yalon eb yuj diosalil bay, yuj tzet max bet yab eb, cꞌal yuj tzet max bet yil eb, yujtol axcacꞌal max yun yal-lay bay eb, caytuꞌ max uji.
—Palta, ¿tzet yuj xan chin e sayicꞌok? ¿Tom man e yojtakok tol a bay yatut in Mam yowalil chin ayji? ẍi bay eb.
—Ach ton tiꞌ, in Cꞌajol ach, cax camcꞌulnebil ach wuj; caw chin tzaloj en, ẍi.
Yujtol chi yalcan yul txꞌan Un Tzꞌibbilcan axca tiꞌ:
—Tzꞌin cachi. Elan yin jun winak tiꞌ, ẍi bay.
Axa yoc matxan kꞌab Cham yin nak tuꞌ.
—A eb cuywom Juan, cham akꞌom bautismo, yetok eb cuywom eb fariseo, xiwil el chi yakꞌ eb cꞌajbancꞌulal, cax chi txajli eb, palta a eb a cuywom ach tiꞌ, ¿tzet yuj xan asan loj chi yun eb? ẍi eb bay.
Ay jun chi yik Judas, yuẍtak Jacobo, yetok cꞌapax Judas Iscariote, nak max aon oc Jesús yul kꞌab camich.
A mac watxꞌ is nabal, watxꞌ tzet chi el yuneni, yujtol asan tzet yetal watxꞌ ay yin is nabal. A pax eb yob is nabal xin, yob cꞌapax tzet chi el yunen eb, yujtol asan tzet yob ay yin is nabal eb, yujtol a tzet ay yin co nabal, aꞌ chi jalaꞌ.
—A Juan cham akꞌom bautismo cheknejontek ayach. Chi ul co kꞌanlej ayach ta ach Cristo ach, a ton Cham lanan jechbanen jayi, ma txꞌok junokxa chi jechbanej jay xin, ẍi eb bay.
Maj a tzꞌubil in ti tiꞌ yuj a txꞌoxkꞌabnen el a camcꞌulal, palta jun ix tiꞌ, yecheltaxcꞌal in jay caytiꞌ, cꞌamcꞌal chi bek tzꞌubon el wakan.
Axa yalon bay eb ayicꞌ tuꞌ axca tiꞌ:
Max lajwi tuꞌ, max paxicꞌ Jesús bay junxa kꞌaxepal aꞌ mar bay petojtaꞌa. A yet max ecꞌapnok tuꞌ, max tzaloj aj eb anima masanil bay tuꞌ, yujtol caw wal echbanebilxacꞌal yuj eb.
Ta ay mac cꞌam chex chaoni, chex el yul is conob eb tuꞌ. Che tziccan el pokokal e yakan yuj e txꞌoxkꞌabnen elok tol cꞌamxa e yalon e yet yin eb, cax chex toji, ẍi Jesús bay eb.
Wal yel chi wal ayex, ay jaywan e xol, mac ex ayex ecꞌ tiꞌ, manto ex camok okto e yil yoccan Dios yin yajawil, ẍi Jesús bay eb.
—Cꞌam chi jeꞌ e tenon oc wanaj nak, yujtol a eb man ajcꞌulok oc jin, a jetok ayoc eb, ẍi bay.
A pokokal jun e conob chi occan yin jakan tiꞌ, ti chi co tziccan el on, yuj co txꞌoxkꞌabnen el tol cꞌamxa jalon jet e yin; palta nachajokab el e yuj, tol toxa ok occan Dios yin Yajawil, quex chican bay eb.
A tinani xin, ay jun chin kꞌanlej ayach. A nak max makꞌlay yuj eb elkꞌom tuꞌ, ¿mac junok eb oxwan tuꞌ caw yel yet animail nak cha naꞌ? ẍi Jesús bay cham meẍtol yin ley Moisés tuꞌ.
Cayton cꞌapax tuꞌ Satanás, ta chi pojchaj yetok eb yet espíritual yob tuꞌ, ¿xin ta chi mayji yikbej? Chi wal juntzan tiꞌ ayex, yujtol ayin tiꞌ che yalaꞌ tol yuj yikbej Beelzebú chi wioncan el eb yet espíritual yob.
—Meẍtol, a yet max alon juntzan tiꞌ, ayon tiꞌ man watxꞌok max jab cꞌapaxok, ẍi cham bay.
Max lajwi tuꞌ, max naon pax nak axca tiꞌ: ¡A…, tix ok wut tiꞌ! Ok wuchay juntzan in cꞌuna tiꞌ, cax ok in watxꞌnen juntzanokxa mimek ok wutej. A tuꞌ ok in wajbaj sat wawoj tiꞌ, cꞌal masanil tzet ay ayin.
Palta kꞌinalok ta ay junokxa mosejal man yojtakok, cax chi watxꞌnen juntzan tzet yetal tol moj yikon tzꞌum yuj. A jun tuꞌ, txennej tzꞌum ok yikaꞌ. A eb miman tzet akꞌbil bay, miman tzet ok kꞌanlay el bay eb. Yetok eb miman tzet abenebilcan bay, yowalil miman tzet ok yakꞌ cꞌapax eb.
A yet max yalon axca tuꞌ, masanil eb ajcꞌul oc yin Cham, max qꞌuixwi aj eb; palta masanil eb anima xin, caw wal max tzaloj eb yilon juntzan tzet cꞌayubtak chi el yunen Cham.
Max yilon Jesús, tzet max yut ba eb awtebil low yetok bay jun loj tuꞌ, tol a bay chi ay chotan eb mimek winak, a tuꞌ chi ay chotan eb. Yuj tuꞌ max yal bay eb axca tiꞌ:
Cꞌamxa yopiso. Caxcꞌal chi alay ay sat txꞌotxꞌ, caxcꞌal chi toj somilok abono, tutun cꞌamxa yopiso. Toxacꞌal chi kꞌoklay elok. A juntzan max e yab tiꞌ, naobtanejek sicꞌlibil, ẍi Jesús bay eb.
Palta max yal nak bay is mam tuꞌ axca tiꞌ: Ojtak, mimanxa tiempocꞌal ach wakꞌon serbil. Cꞌam junelok cꞌam chi wikej bay chalaꞌ. Tok yuj tuꞌ cax ayxa bay chakꞌ junok in chiwo in chiꞌ yetok eb wamigo yin junok in kꞌin.
bay ayicꞌ owan wuẍtak. Chi toj yalon yab eb, yet watxꞌ cꞌam chi jay eb wetok xol yailal bay ayin ecꞌ tiꞌ, ẍi cham.
Ay juntzan eb fariseo max kꞌanlen bay Jesús axca tiꞌ:
Ay cawan winak max bet txajlok bay templo Dios. Fariseo jun, tekom el tojlabal junxa.
A yet lanan yapni oc Jesús bay conob Jericó, ay jun nak cꞌam chi jeꞌ yilwi, chotan ay ti be. Lanan kꞌanon sabal bay anima chi ecꞌ yul be tuꞌ.
Axa yalon cham bay tuꞌ: Watxꞌ xin. Ach tiꞌ caw wal watxꞌ ach ayin. Caxcꞌal txenchꞌan max wakꞌcan ayach, palta watxꞌcꞌal max ot a nabal yetok. Yuj tuꞌ xan ti chi waoc opiso yin yajawilal yiban lajonebok conob, ẍi bay.
Xan ay wal jun tiempoal ok jayok, axa eb ajcꞌul yin jun conob tiꞌ, ok corralnej aj eb. Ok oymoj eb yinlak, axa yakꞌon eb owal yin tuꞌ.
Tzancꞌal mac chi makꞌay ba yiban jun chꞌen tuꞌ, cocꞌxacꞌal chi yun kꞌajtok. Axa junok mactxel chi aycꞌay jun chꞌen tuꞌ yiban, cocꞌxacꞌal chi yuncan yuj chꞌen, ẍi Jesús bay eb.
masantacꞌal ok wacan oc eb ajcꞌul oc en batxlubok akan, ẍi Dios bay Cham Wajawil, ẍi David.
Ay juntzan yechelej ok txꞌox ba yin cꞌu, cꞌal yin xajaw, cꞌal yin waycan. A bay sat txꞌotxꞌ tiꞌ xin, ok somchaj el cꞌul anima bay junjun conob yuj xiwilal, yujtol ok aj wan aꞌ mar cax ok awjok makꞌon ay ba aꞌ.
Yujtol chi wal ayex, cꞌamxa bakꞌin ok in low yet kꞌin Pascua tiꞌ junelokxa, masantacꞌal ok oc junokxa Pascua bay ok occan Dios Yajawil, ẍi bay eb.
—Kꞌokbil, ẍi Cham bay eb.
—Cꞌamak cha, man wet beyomok in ba yetok eb, ẍi bay nak.
Axa max yabeni tol aj Galilea toni, xan max yatok bay Herodes, yujtol a cham tuꞌ yajaw yayji bay Galilea tuꞌ. A yet tuꞌ, ayicꞌ cham cab oxeb cꞌual bay Jerusalén.
A yet lanan curusnelay Cham yuj eb, max yalon axca tiꞌ:
A eb ix tzaklojnak yintak Jesús bay Galilea, max bet yil eb chꞌen chꞌen tuꞌ. Max bet yilon eb tzetbil max yun yalaycan octok is mimanil Cham yul chꞌen.
Yuj tuꞌ xan max yal Jesús bay eb;
—A yul txꞌan Un tzꞌibbilcan wabixal ayin Cristo in tiꞌ, tol yowalil ok in camok, cax chin ictzoj pax aj xol eb camnak yet cabjial.
—Cꞌamak, mayinnak, ẍi bay eb.
Lajwicꞌal kꞌanjab Andrés tuꞌ yetok Jesús, max toj sayon ecꞌ jun yuẍtak tuꞌ. Axa yet max ilchaj yuj, max yalon bay axca tiꞌ:
—Akꞌek noj juntzan net tiꞌ yetok aej, ẍi bay eb.
Axa kꞌanlen Nicodemo tuꞌ bay axca tiꞌ:
A jun aynaktek satcan, yajaw yayji yiban masanil anima. Axa ayon aj yulyibankꞌinal on tiꞌ, anima oncꞌal el co masanil. Asan yet yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ chi jalaꞌ. Palta jun aynaktek satcan tu xin, Yajaw yayji jiban co masanil.
Lajwicꞌal yaben ix tzet max yal Jesús bay, max yalon ix bay Cham:
—A yet babelal, a yuj tzet max al ayon, xan max jaoc co cꞌul yin Jesús. Axa tinani xin, a wal caw Cham max alon ayon. Yuj tuꞌ xan max co watxꞌ anejxacꞌal oc co cꞌul yin tinaniꞌ, caw wal jojtakxa sicꞌlibil, tol a Cham tiꞌ, wal yel, a ton co Colomal co masanil ayon cajan on bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, ẍi eb bay ix.
—A Cham max akꞌon jaycan in cꞌul, a max alon ayin axca tiꞌ: Iaj a wayub, beyan, ẍi ayin, ẍi nak bay eb.
Yelcꞌulal ton che cuy txꞌan Un Tzꞌibbilcanok, yujtol a e naoni, tol a tuꞌ ok ilchaj e kꞌinal tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal, palta caxcꞌal chi yaltek txꞌan Un tuꞌ wabixal,
Max oc eb yul barco, max tꞌinlonen ecꞌtok ba eb bay conob Capernaum bay ti aꞌ mar tuꞌ. Caw wal kꞌektaninakxa yet max toj eb. A pax Jesús xin, cꞌamto chi jay bay eb.
A yet max yaben aj eb aj Judea juntzan tuꞌ, yob max yal eb yin, yujtol max yal Jesús jun tiꞌ: Ayin ton axca loj wayji, cax a bay satcan max in aytek, ẍi bay eb.
Max yalon cꞌapax axca tiꞌ:
—A juntzan cuybanilej chi wal ayex tiꞌ, man wetok, palta yet Cham max in chekontek.
Caytuꞌ max yut yalon axca tuꞌ, yujtol a eb chi yaoc cꞌul yin Cham, chi cajbaj oc Cham Espíritu yin eb. A yet jun tiempoal tuꞌ, cꞌamto chi akꞌlay Espíritu bay eb anima, yujtol manto paxaj Jesús bay satcan.
—Ta ay junok ex cꞌam jabok e mul, aokab jun tuꞌ chi babji kꞌokon oc chꞌen chꞌen yin ix, ẍi bay eb.
Xiwiltocꞌal tzet chi jeꞌ walontek e yin cꞌal ex in beycꞌulneni. Palta a Cham cheknejintek, caw wal yel chi yalaꞌ. A tzet yalnak ayin, asan chi walaꞌ, ẍi bay eb.
Wal yel chi wal ayex, a mac chi iken tzet chi walaꞌ, cꞌam bakꞌin ok cam eb, ẍi Jesús bay eb.
Lajwi tuꞌ, max ilaytok nak yuj eb bay eb fariseo.
Kꞌinalok ta man chekbejok Dios Jesús tuꞌ, cꞌam mi jabok tzet chi jeꞌ yuj, ẍi nak bay eb.
A yet max yalon juntzan tiꞌ, max teyelen aj ba eb aj Judea tuꞌ yuj. Ca pojan max yut ba eb junelxa.
A bay jun aldea chi yik Betania, ay jun winak max yaban ayok, chi yik Lázaro. Ay cawan yanab jun winak tuꞌ, ay jun chi yik María, ay junxa chi yik Marta. Aj Betaniacꞌal el eb yoxwanil.
—A nak a nuej tuꞌ, ok ictzoj aj nak, ẍi Jesús bay ix.
Axa yeltek nak camnak tuꞌ. Chulan oc juntzan kꞌapej yin yakan nak cꞌal yin is kꞌab nak. Ay cꞌapax jun an xotan oc yalan is tiꞌ. Max yal Jesús axca tiꞌ:
—Yuj wal dios. Al-layokab watxꞌ kꞌanej bay Cham chekbiltek yuj Cham Jajawil tiꞌ. Jalek watxꞌ kꞌanej bay Cham co Reyal ayon israel on tiꞌ, ẍi eb.
Axa yalon bay eb axca tiꞌ:
Yojtakxa mactxel jun ok aon oc yul kꞌab camich. Yuj tuꞌ xan max yal axca tiꞌ: Man e masanilok max watxꞌji e nabal, ẍi.
Ta che camcꞌulnelej e ba junjun ex, ok yojtaknej el masanil eb anima, tol yel toni in cuywom ex, ẍi Jesús bay eb.
Ay junxa mac chi yik cꞌapax Judas, manak Judas Iscariote, aꞌ max alon bay Cham axca tiꞌ:
Kꞌinalok ta yet ex yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ yetok eb, tekan chex camcꞌulnej eb; palta mayexxa yetok yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, yujtol toxa max ex in siqꞌuil xol eb. Yuj tuꞌ xan chi chichon oc cꞌul eb e yin, yujtol manxa e yetbiok e ba yetok eb.
Kꞌinalok junok ix ix tinaniꞌ, lanan yalji yuneꞌ. Yaꞌ ton chi yabej, yujtol lanan yecꞌ yaꞌ, palta a yet mayal jay yuneꞌ tuꞌ, tok naanto yailal tuꞌ yuj; a ti yet, caw wal chi tzaloji, yujtol mayal jay jun unin yuj bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ.
Cha pojcan el eb, yuj yoccan eb etok, yuj a kꞌanej tol yel chi yalaꞌ.
Axa pax Pedro xin, max cancan ti puerta. Axa jun cuywom Jesús max elol bay lecancan oc Pedro tuꞌ, cax max yalon bay ix makom ti na tuꞌ, tol chi octek Pedro tuꞌ yetok eb.
—¿Yulcꞌal mi et chi tita, xan cha kꞌanlej el jun tiꞌ ayin, ma ay mac max alon ayach? ẍi Jesús bay.
Yuj tuꞌ xan max yal bay axca tiꞌ:
Yuj tu xin, xan a jun is cuywom tuꞌ max ioncantok xal txutxej tuꞌ yetok bay yatut, cax max ayji ecꞌ xal yintak.
A pax María aj Magdala tu xin, max cancan cꞌatan jun chꞌen tuꞌ. Maj octok ix yul chꞌen. Tocꞌal max octok tꞌanan ix yul, cax chi okꞌ ix.
Lajwi tuꞌ, axa yalon bay Tomás tuꞌ axca tiꞌ:
Axa jitzontek ba Jesús cꞌatan eb tuꞌ, max yion aj ixim pan tuꞌ, max cꞌoli pojon ecꞌ xol eb, cax max pojon cꞌapax ecꞌ no txay tuꞌ.
Yel toni, a Juan max akꞌwi bautizar yetok aej, palta a yet jayeb cꞌu, ok akꞌlay Cham Espíritu Santo ayex, cax ok ex akꞌlay bautizar yuj, ẍi Jesús.
A yet jun tiempoal tuꞌ, ay eb israel ayicꞌ bay Jerusalén tuꞌ, txꞌok txꞌokcꞌal lugaril titnak eb bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ. A ton wal bay Dios chi yal ba eb.
Ayokto max yojtaknen el David tuꞌ, tzet ok eloc Cham Cristo. Yuj tuꞌ xan yalnakcanok, tol tꞌinan yictzonelay aj Cham. Yalnakcanok tol man ok beklaycan yuj Dios xol eb camnak, cax man ok chalay kꞌatok is mimanil cꞌapaxok.
Max yil masanil eb anima ayicꞌ bay tuꞌ bey nak. Max yab cꞌapax eb yalon nak is watxꞌ kꞌanej bay Dios,
Cꞌam junokxa mac chi jeꞌ co colchaj yuj, yujtol a bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, cꞌam junok mactxel max yakꞌ Dios yopiso yakꞌon colbanilej, palta asannej Jesús, ẍi Pedro.
Axa yalon Pedro bay Ananías tuꞌ:
—Max cam jalon ayex tol cꞌamxa che yalil cuybej Jesús tuꞌ. Palta ilab tinaniꞌ, pilan mayal saklem jun e cuybej tiꞌ bay Jerusalén tiꞌ. Toltax che yochej che yatok camichal Jesús tuꞌ jiban, ẍi bay eb.
Lajwi tu xin, max sayon eb jaywanxa mac chi aon oc tzꞌakbal kꞌanej yiban Esteban tuꞌ. Max jaycꞌal eb, max yalon eb bay eb yajaw tuꞌ:
Axa tenlaytok Moisés tuꞌ yuj nak tol yelcꞌulal wal chi akꞌwi owal tuꞌ, max yalon nak bay axca tiꞌ: ¿Mac max ach aon oc yajawil, cꞌal yin juezal co xol on?
—Ilabi, jakan puertail satcan chi wilaꞌ. Ayicꞌ Cham Chekbiltek yuj Dios co xol bay is watxꞌ kꞌab, ẍi.
Yujtol chi wilaꞌ tol caw wal ayoc sawenal en, cax asan tzet man watxꞌok lanan akꞌon serbil, ẍi Pedro tuꞌ bay.
A pax eb ajun yetok Saulo tu xin, caw wal max cꞌaycan el cꞌul eb. Max yab eb yoc jun nukꞌej tuꞌ, palta cꞌam mac max yil eb yin.
—Eneas, a Jesucristo chi akꞌon jaycan a cꞌul. Yuj tu xin, ajan wanok, iaj a wayub, ẍi bay nak.
—¿A mi caytiꞌ ayicꞌ Simón, nak chi yik cꞌapax Pedro? ẍi eb.
Yet payxa, ayokto max yaloncan el eb chekbej Dios yabixal Jesús. Yalnakcan junjun eb, tol masanilcꞌal mac ok yaoc cꞌul yin, ok akꞌlaycan lajwok yobtakil eb yuj, ẍi Pedro bay eb.
A yet max apniocok, max yiloni, xiwil watxꞌcꞌulal Dios max yakꞌ yiban eb tuꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ, caw wal max yiꞌ is tzalojcꞌulal yin eb, max cꞌoli yiptzelay eb masanil yuj. Max yalon bay eb, tol caw wal tecꞌancꞌal chi yut ba eb, cax chi yaoncꞌal oc eb cꞌul yin Cham Jajawil.
Axa max kꞌinibi aj junxa cꞌual, axacꞌal chi yal eb soldado, yujtol maj nachaj el yuj eb, bay max ca toj Pedro tuꞌ.
A yin masanil juntzan tiꞌ max ecꞌ 450 abil. Lajwi tuꞌ max yaon oc Dios juntzan eb juez yuj yakꞌwi cuenta eb masantacꞌal yul is tiempoal Samuel is chekbej.
Xan cacꞌal tuꞌ max yun saklem kꞌanej Cham Jajawil bay masanil jun lugar tuꞌ.
Max lajwi tuꞌ, max eqꞌuel Pablo yetok Bernabé yul yet Pisidia, cax max apni eb yul yet Panfilia.
A eb max cheklaytok toj yakꞌ txꞌan carta tuꞌ. Max yaltok eb yul txꞌan axca tiꞌ:
Lajwi tu xin, cax max on toji, max on apni bay conob Filipos. A jun conob tuꞌ, yet eb aj Roma. Miman yelapnok jun conob tuꞌ yintak juntzanxa ay yul yet Macedonia tuꞌ. Txꞌialcꞌal cꞌual max on ayji ecꞌ bay jun conob tuꞌ.
Max yion octok nak eb bay is na, max low eb yuj nak. Caw wal chi tzaloj nak yetokcꞌal eb cajan bay is na tuꞌ, yujtol max yaoc eb cꞌul yin Dios.
Ay juntzan winak caw wal chi cuy wal eb jelanil, eb chi yik epicúreo yetok juntzan eb chi yik estoico, max cꞌoli kꞌanjab eb yetok Pablo. Axa nanxa eb xin, max yalubtanen eb axca tiꞌ:
Lajwi yalon axca tuꞌ, max eltek yul nail culto eb tuꞌ, axa toj bay yatut jun cham chi ikon Ticio Justo. Man israelok cham, palta chi yiay ba cham bay Dios. Cawilal nail culto tuꞌ ay yatut cham.
Yuj tuꞌ xan max yal pax bay eb axca tiꞌ:
Txꞌok txꞌokxacꞌal tzet chi yal eb anima wajan oc tuꞌ, yujtol sombinak ay is nabal eb. Ecꞌban nan eb man yojtakok, tzet yuj xan wajan ecꞌ eb.
Max wal bay eb wet israelal, cꞌal bay eb man israelok, tol yowalil chi na ba eb satak Dios, cax chi yaon oc eb cꞌul yin Cham Jajawil Jesucristo.
A yet max jaben yetok eb aj Cesarea tzet chi yal cham tuꞌ, max on oc tean yin Pablo, tol cꞌam chi toj bay Jerusalén tuꞌ.
Axa yalon cham bay axca tiꞌ:
A yet max yilon cham coronel tuꞌ axca tuꞌ, max yakꞌ cham ilay octok Pablo tuꞌ yul cuartel. Max chekon cham tol chi makꞌlayi, yet watxꞌ chi yalajok tzet yuj xan chi aj weknaj eb anima tuꞌ, cax chi tit yowal eb yin.
Ecꞌban 40 bisil eb max alon axca tuꞌ.
Lajwi tuꞌ, max yakꞌon cham taynelay bay is miman na cham rey Herodes.
Axa yapni oc cham Festo tuꞌ bay conob Cesarea tuꞌ yuj chaon yopiso yin yoccan yin yajawil. Cabjiixto chaon cham yopiso tuꞌ, max toj cham bay Jerusalén.
Lajwi tuꞌ max yalon axca tiꞌ:
—Caw wal loco ach Pablo. Xiwil tzet chi akꞌi a cuyuꞌ, yuj tuꞌ xan chach oc locoal yuj, ẍi bay.
Lajwi co tokꞌon ajtek teꞌ xin, axa cꞌaloncan cawxok eb mulnajwom yin barco teꞌ miman tuꞌ yetok mimek lasu. Tutun chi xiw eb talaj cꞌuxan chi makꞌay ba te barco tuꞌ yiban jun makan arena chi yik Sirte bay melemal aꞌ tuꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ xan max xuyaytek eb an kꞌap bay chi low cakꞌekꞌ. Lajwi tuꞌ max on cancꞌal axca tuꞌ. Munilxacꞌal max ilaytok teꞌ jalan yuj cakꞌekꞌ.
Axa yet maxax on colchaj el xin, max jabeni tol Malta bi jun lugar nan aꞌ tuꞌ.
28-29 Yuj tu xin, nachajokab el e yuj, tol lanan yakꞌon Dios jun colbanilej tiꞌ bay eb man israelok. Yujtol chi yacbaj eb tuꞌ txiquin bay, ẍi Pablo bay eb.
Kꞌaynak eb yetok masanil is yob nabal yetok ajmulal, xan acꞌalaꞌ naon eb tzet man watxꞌok. Pekꞌ eb yin tzet man watxꞌok. Caw yob eb. Chi yochej oc eb tzet ay bay junokxa mactxel. Makꞌom cam anima cꞌapax eb. Akꞌom owal eb. Etnem anima eb. Caw wal yob is beybal eb. Alom kꞌumal eb.
Manak eb chi yik judío yujcꞌal yinatil, manak eb tuꞌ yel wali judío yul sat Dios. Manak eb ayoc jun circuncisión tuꞌ yin, manak eb tuꞌ yel wali ayoc yechel yul sat Dios.
A tinaniꞌ, ¿xin ta chi jeꞌ co maynen co ba che naꞌ? Tutun wal cꞌam chi jeꞌ, yujtol man yujok chi jikej ley Moisés xan chon colchaji, palta asan wal yuj chi jaoc co cꞌul yin Jesús, xan chon colchaji. Yuj tu xin, maj jeꞌ co maynen co ba.
A tinaniꞌ, toxa mayal yal Dios, tol watxꞌ on yul sat, yujtol chi jaoc co cꞌul yin. Yuj tuꞌ, juncꞌulalxa ayon yetok, yujcꞌal Cham Jajawil Jesucristo.
Cayokab on tuꞌ, nachajokab el juj, tol camnak onxa, cꞌamxa yalon yet yobtakil jin. Co naek cꞌapaxok, tol iquis on, yuj jakꞌon serbil Dios, yujtol junxanej jayji yetok Cristo Jesús.
Cꞌam chi wun tzet watxꞌ axca wal chi wochej tuꞌ. A tzet man watxꞌok, cꞌam chi wochej tuꞌ, a chi wuncꞌal.
Acꞌalaꞌ cꞌapax Cham Yespíritu Dios, caw wal chi oc Cham jetok bay man tzꞌakanok co nabal. Yujtol man jojtakok tzet chi jut txajlok co ba axca chi yochej Dios. Ay bay tocꞌal chon sikꞌson aj jay co cꞌul, yujtol cꞌam chi nachaj juj tzet chi jut jalon co ba bay Dios. Palta axa Cham Espíritu chi txajli juj yin co kꞌakawil tuꞌ.
Palta tekan ayex ok e yal axca tiꞌ ayin: Ta axca tu xin, ¿tzet yuj xan chi yal pax Dios tol ayon yobtakwom on xin? ¿Mac junok chi jeꞌ tenon oc wanaj tzet chi yochej Dios? tekan quex chi.
Palta a eb manchak yaoc cꞌul yin Cham Jajawil, ¿tzet ok yut yalon ba eb bay? ¿tzet ok yut yaon oc eb cꞌul yin, ta manchak yab eb yabixal? Yetok cꞌapaxok, ¿tzet ok yut yaben eb yabixal, ta cꞌam mac chi alon yabixal bay eb?
Yel toni, axca ton tol tzocꞌbil el eb wet conob tuꞌ, yujtol maj yaoc eb cꞌul yin Dios. Axa ex pax xin, yuj che yaoc e cꞌul yin, xan max quex occan qꞌuexelok eb. Yuj tuꞌ, xe yi talaj aj can e ba, taynejekcꞌal e ba.
Tzalojokonek yetok eb chi tzaloji. Cusokonek yetok eb chi cusi.
Yujtol chi yal yul txꞌan Un axca tiꞌ:
Ex wuẍtak, ex wanab, wojtak sicꞌlibil tol watxꞌ e nabal, cax caw jelan ex yin yet Dios. Wojtak tol caw chi jeꞌ e yalen oc e nabal e xol bay tuꞌ.
Chi wa cꞌapaxtok cawil cꞌul janab Trifena yetok Trifosa, eb tol caw chi mulnaj yin yobra Cham Jajawil. Chi wa cꞌapaxtok cawil cꞌul janab Pérsida. Caw ay in camcꞌulal yin, yujtol caw chi yiajtek cꞌulok mulnaj yin yobra Cham Jajawil.
Manwalnak akꞌoj bautizar tuꞌ wopiso yuj Cristo, palta a aloj el kꞌanejal yet colbanilej. Manak yetok kꞌanejal jelanilal walnak jun abix tuꞌ, yet watxꞌ aokab camichal Cristo yin curus miman yelapnok yul sat eb chi abxalwi tuꞌ.
A eb cꞌam oc Yespíritu Dios yin, cꞌam chi cha yab eb cuybej Cham Espíritu yujtol cꞌam yelapnok yul sat eb. Cꞌam chi jeꞌ comon chi nachaj el juntzan cuybej tuꞌ yuj eb, yujtol asan Cham Yespíritu Dios chi akꞌon nachaj elok.
Yuj tu xin, cꞌam chi jeꞌ e beycꞌulnen junok mactxel tinaniꞌ. Jechbanejek ato yet ok jay Cham Jajawil, yujtol a Cham ok txꞌoxon el masanil tzet yetal. Axca junok tzet yetal eban el xol kꞌekkꞌinal, axa chi oc jopnaj sakkꞌinal yin, cax masanilxacꞌal chi txecloj elok, cayton tuꞌ ok yun txecloj el masanil tzet yetal yet tuꞌ. A Cham Jajawil ok akꞌon txecloj el tzetak yetal ay yin co nabal co masanil. Catatuꞌ ok al-lay watxꞌ kꞌanej yin junjun yuj Dios, atacꞌalaꞌ co mulnajil junjun on.
¿Tom manto e yojtakok cꞌapaxok, tol ayon cꞌapax ok co beycꞌulnej eb ángel? Yuj tuꞌ xan a juntzan tzet yetal yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, moj cꞌapax co watxꞌnen yayji.
Yujtol caxcꞌal man creyenteok nak yichamil ix tuꞌ, palta axca tol yet Dios yayji nak yetok ix, yujtol junnejxa yayji nak yetok ix creyente tuꞌ. Acꞌalaꞌ cꞌapax junok ix man creyenteok, axca tol yet-xa Dios yayji ix, yujtol junxanej yayji ix yetok nak creyente tuꞌ. Kꞌinalok ta axca tol man yetok Dios eb cawanil, comon anima mi yayji yuninal eb, palta cꞌamak; yet cꞌapax Dios eb unin tuꞌ.
Ay tzet chi al-lay oc diosal chi ecꞌ satcan. Ay cꞌapax tzet chi al-lay oc diosal yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ. Yujtol a eb anima, xiwil tzet chi yaloc is diosalok, cꞌal yajawilok.
Acꞌalaꞌ yet ayin ecꞌ yetok eb man tecꞌanok waay is nabal, lajan chi wut in ba yetok eb. Axca tol man tecꞌanok waay in nabal, caytuꞌ chi wut in ba, yuj in monten jaywanok eb. Xan tzancꞌal bay chin eqꞌui, axcacꞌal chi yut ba eb bay chin ecꞌ tuꞌ, caytuꞌ chi wut in ba yetok eb, yet watxꞌ ta cꞌuxan ay eb chi chaꞌ is colbanil wuj.
Yujtol a Cham Jajawil ay yet txꞌotxꞌ txꞌotxꞌ tiꞌ, cꞌal masanil tzet yetal ibil aj yuj txꞌotxꞌ, cꞌal eb cajyom bay.
A juntzan cuybanil yuj tzet chi yun chalay cena walnakcan ayex, a Cham Jajawil akꞌnejcan ayin. A ton juntzan ok waltok ayex tiꞌ. A yet jun akꞌbal yet max alay oc Cham Jajawil Jesús yul kꞌab eb tꞌinantaꞌ yakꞌon camok, a yet manto michchajok, max yion aj jun ixim pan.
Jojtak tol xiwil yetbeyom co mimanil tiꞌ, palta junnej yayji masanil.
Jieltek co nabal yin juntzanok son tinaniꞌ. Kꞌinalok ta chi xulay chirima, ma chi txal-lay pax junok arpa, ta toxacꞌal chi somlabi nukꞌ, ¿xin ta chi jab tzet bital chi yaoc junjun?
Ta ayex che naꞌ, tol ay e yopiso e yalon el kꞌanej Dios, ma che naꞌ tol chi mulnaj oc Cham Yespíritu Dios e yin, ojtaknejek elok, tol chekbanil Cham Jajawil juntzan chin tzꞌibejtok ayex tiꞌ.
A yet mayal yacan oc Cham masanil tzetak yetal yul kꞌab is Cꞌajol tuꞌ, catatuꞌ a wal caw Cham Cꞌajolej tuꞌ ok yaoc ba yul kꞌab is Mam, Cham beknej oc masanil tzetak yetal tuꞌ yul is kꞌab. Catatu bian, asanxanej Dios ok yajawbok yiban masanil.
A tinaniꞌ ok waltok e yab yuj jun ofrenda lanan yilay aj co xol tiꞌ, cax ok alaytok bay eb jet creyenteal. A juntzan chekbanil ok waltok ayex tiꞌ, albilxa wuj bay juntzan iglesia bay yul yet Galacia. Yuj tuꞌ, axcaokab yunnak eb tuꞌ, cayokab tuꞌ che yun cꞌapax ayex tiꞌ.
Ex wuẍtak, ex wanab, chi jochej che yojtaknej elok, jantak yailal ecꞌ jilnak bay yul yet Asia, yujtol xiwil yailal ecꞌ jilnak bay tuꞌ, xan ijan wal maj techaj juj. A co naoni tol maj onxa colchaj el yul kꞌab camich.
Axca yoc jab junok incienso chi yakꞌ Cristo bay Dios, caw sukꞌukꞌi jab, cayon tuꞌ yet lanan ecꞌ jalon el yabixal bay eb lanan colchaji, cꞌal bay eb lananto cꞌayicꞌok.
Yakꞌban iquis on, chacꞌantek camich jiban on masanil tiempo, yujtol junxanej jayji yetok Jesús. Yuj tuꞌ, caxcꞌal ok cam co mimanil tiꞌ on, palta lanan txecloj el is kꞌinal Jesús yin co mimanil cambejal yayji tiꞌ.
A yet max ajapnok tiempoal in txꞌoxon in watxꞌcꞌulal max waben e tewilal. A yet max ajapnok cꞌual colbanilej, max in oc e yetok, ẍi Dios.
Palta ayex tiꞌ, max ex cus axca chi yochej Dios. Yuj tuꞌ naektek, tzet max yun e yeloc yuj. Caw yelcꞌulal wal tol max ex oc il, cax max e yalontek tzet max el e yunen yuj e colon e ba. Max tit e yowal yuj jun tzet max uj e xol tuꞌ, max ex xiw cꞌapax aj yuj. Xiwil max e yochej max ex kꞌanjab wetok. Max el yin e cꞌul e yakꞌon cuenta nak max oc is yobtakil tuꞌ yuj e txꞌoxkꞌabnen elok tol cꞌam e locanil yin jun is mul nak tuꞌ.
Yujtol wojtakxa, tol caw wal che yochej chex colwaj bay eb. Lanan ex walon watxꞌil bay eb aj Macedonia tiꞌ. Tix chi wut kꞌanjab in ba e yin bay eb axca tiꞌ: A eb creyente yul yet Acaya, junxa abilcꞌal cꞌoli eb yakꞌon yofrenda, quin chi. Axa yet max yaben eb aj Macedonia tiꞌ, tol yelcꞌulal wal lanan e yakꞌoni, cax xiwil eb max bulchaj yakꞌon yet.
Man yujok tzet chi junej xan chi jakꞌ tzalojbok co cꞌul; palta jakꞌek tzalojbok co cꞌul yuj tzet chi yun Cham Jajawil.
Ta ay mac cꞌamto chi yiꞌ yip yin is creyenteal, caw chin oc il yuj eb, axca tol cꞌamto chi wiꞌ cꞌapax wip yetok eb. Ta ay eb chi akꞌlay etax el is nabal, caw chi oc pitzꞌan yail yin in cꞌul sicꞌlibil.
Palta chi wochej tol caw che yojtaknej elok, tol ayon tiꞌ, acaw creyente on sicꞌlibil.
Acꞌal wabixal chixa yab eb, yujtol ay eb max yal wuj axca tiꞌ: A jun winak max con etnen yet yalan, yujtol max yochej tol cꞌam chi jaoc co cꞌul yin Cristo, axa tinani xin, axa jun chi ecꞌ alon el yabixal, ẍi eb wuj.
Yuj tuꞌ, ta chi jaoc co cꞌul yin Dios, lajan chi jut co chaon is watxꞌcꞌulal tuꞌ axca yutnak chaon Abraham tuꞌ, yujtol yanak oc yin cꞌul.
Ex wuẍtak, ex wanab, chin tewitok ayex, tol lajanokab che yut e nabal wetok, yujtol ayin tiꞌ, lajan max wut in nabal e yetok yet max in ecꞌ ayex tuꞌ. Watxꞌcꞌal max e yut e ba ayin.
A pax ayin tiꞌ ex wuẍtak, ex wanab, kꞌinalok ta acꞌalaꞌto waloni tol yowalil chi akꞌlay circuncidar junok mactxel, maj mi incꞌaltaꞌ yuktej ecꞌ eb wet israelal. Kꞌinalok ta caytuꞌ chi wut cuywaj in ba axca tuꞌ, cꞌam mi chi chichon oc cꞌul eb yin yabixal Cristo yin te curus.
Masanilcꞌal mac chi beybalnen juntzan cuybanilej tiꞌ, a ton eb tuꞌ yel wali, israel eb yul sat Dios, yujtol is conob yayji eb. Yakꞌokab Dios juncꞌulal bay eb, cax okꞌokab cꞌul yin eb cꞌapaxok.
Aꞌ max con ictzonen aj yetok Cristo Jesús. Chotan onxa ay satcan yetok Cristo yul sat tinaniꞌ.
Aꞌ ayoc yin txꞌoxbanilejal masanil makanil eb mamej bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, cꞌal bay satcan.
Yowalil che chaꞌ qꞌuexchaj e nabal, che chaon junok acꞌ nabalej chi watxꞌnej Dios axca chi yochej. Ta axca tu xin, tutun wal yel, watxꞌ tzet ok e beybalnej, cax watxꞌcꞌal ok e yut e ba.
Ex istzilej, yikem che yut e ba bay e yichamil junjun ex, axca che yut e ba bay Cham Jajawil.
A Dios akꞌnej wopiso walon el jun abix tiꞌ. Preso wayji tinaniꞌ yujcꞌal tol chi walilok. Yuj tuꞌ, txajlanek wuj, yet watxꞌ tecꞌanokab in yin walon el axca chi yochej Dios.
Manchak ex xiw bay eb chi chichon oc cꞌul jin. Caytuꞌ ok e yut e txꞌoxkꞌabnen elok, tol ok cꞌaycan el eb yin junelnej. Yetok cꞌapaxok, caytuꞌ ok yun txecloj elok, tol ayxa co colbanil, yujtol caytuꞌ ok yut Dios txꞌoxkꞌabnen elok.
Chaek apnok nak yin tzalojcꞌulal e nan e xol tuꞌ, yujtol e yuẍtak cꞌapax e ba yetok nak yin Cham Jajawil. Masanilcꞌal eb lajan nabal axca Epafrodito tiꞌ, ayokab yelapnok eb yul e sat.
Beybalnejek juntzan cuybanilej yetok juntzanxa tzet e yabnakcan ayin. Masanilcꞌal tzet max e yabcan oc ayin, cꞌal tzet max e yil cꞌapax win, aꞌ che beybalnej. Ta axca tuꞌ chi el e yuneni, ok oc Dios e yetok, Cham chi akꞌon co juncꞌulal.
A yet cꞌamto yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, ayxacꞌaltaꞌ ecꞌ Cristo. Yuj Cham, xan watxꞌ yecꞌ masanil tzetak yetal.
Yuj tuꞌ, cꞌamxa chi yaoc eb nabal yin Cristo. Palta axca co jolom, caytuꞌ yayji Cham ayon, yujtol aꞌ chi akꞌon jip. Yuj Cham, xan junxanej chi juncan el co masanil, cax chon aj can axca chi yochej Dios.
Axa ex e masanil, yelcꞌulalokab tol chex txajlicꞌal, cax che yalon yuj diosalil bay Dios.
E yojtak, tol man tocꞌalok max ex ecꞌ jal watxꞌil. Man yujok jion tumin, xan max ecꞌ jalcan el ayex. Chi yil Dios, tol caw wal yel chi jalaꞌ.
A tzet ok waltok ayex, a ton chi yochej Dios tol chi jikej. Yowalil tol asan yin chi jaoc co nabal, cax cꞌam chi jeꞌ co toj yin ajmulal.
Tzalojanekcꞌal.
Palta lananxa mulnaj yobtakil yin ewantakil tinaniꞌ, masantacꞌal ok ilay el mac chi tenon oc wanaj txꞌoxkꞌabnen aj ba tuꞌ.
Caw chi wochej chach can bay conob Efeso tuꞌ, axcataꞌ max wut tewok in ba ayach, yet max in toj bay Macedonia, yujtol chi wochej chi cam wal alon bay juntzan cuywajwom, tol cꞌamokabxa chi cuywaj eb yin txꞌok cuybanilejal.
Manak Adán max ilay aytek sat yuj nak diablo, palta a Eva, xan a ix max aycꞌay yin tenomtakil bay Dios.
Yakꞌban chin apni, akꞌ ep awten txꞌan kꞌanej Dios yab eb. Chakꞌ ep a jekon oc nabal eb, cꞌal a cuyon eb.
A cuybej Cham Jajawil Jesucristo caw yel, palta ay mac cꞌam chi yaoc cꞌul yin juntzan cuybej tuꞌ. Txꞌok cuybej chi el yalon eb. Cꞌam chi yochej eb juntzan cuybej chi alon tzet chi jut jaon oc co nabal yin Dios.
Yuj tuꞌ xan chi wil juntzan yailal chi jay wiban tiꞌ; palta cꞌam jabok chin qꞌuixwi, yujtol caw wojtak Cham ayoc yipok in cꞌul. Wojtak tol ay yipalil Cham taynen tzet max yakꞌ ayin, masantacꞌal chi jay cꞌual jayubal Cristo.
Ay eb comoncꞌal chi teyelej aj ba, palta nabacꞌal toni. Cꞌam jabok yelapnok tzet chi yal eb. Pojil a ba xol eb. Ojtakxa tol owalxa chi yun lajwi aj tzet chi yal eb tuꞌ.
Yujtol max quin beklaycan yuj Demas in txꞌoklil. Max toj bay Tesalónica, yujtol asan tzet yetal ay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ chi yochej. A juẍtak Crescente, a bay Galacia max toji. A pax juẍtak Tito xin, a bay Dalmacia max toji.
Acꞌalaꞌ cꞌapax eb xal ixnamil ix, chal bay eb, tol watxꞌ chi yut eb is beybal, axca wal chi yochej cꞌul Dios. Man comonok chi yal eb kꞌumal yet animail. Manokab uqꞌuemanok eb. Meẍtolokab eb xal yin tzet watxꞌ,
Caw wal chi wal yuj diosalil bay Dios oj, yet chin txajli,
Yiokab ay ba masanil eb wángel bay, ẍi.
Tix in tiꞌ yetok eb wuninal max yakꞌ Dios ayin, ẍi Cristo yul txꞌan Un Tzꞌibbilcan tuꞌ.
Ay bay chi yalcan yuj jun yet is suk cꞌual yul txꞌan Un Tzꞌibbilcanok, chi yalon axca tiꞌ:
A cuybej ya nachaj elok, lajan axca tzet chi loꞌ icham anima. Yuj tuꞌ xan, asan eb tecꞌanxa is nabal chi cuyon juntzan tuꞌ. Yojtakxa eb chi nailok, baytet ay watxꞌ, baytet ay tzet man watxꞌok.
A eb jichmam, max cha eb ley Moisés yul kꞌab eb sacerdote yinatil Aarón, tol titnak yin Leví. Kꞌinalok ta yuj eb chi jeꞌ watxꞌji oc eb conob satak Dios, ta axca tuꞌ, ¿tzetto wal yuj max oc junxa sacerdote axca Melquisedec, cax man axcaok Aarón?
Cꞌamxa junok ok yal bay yet conob: Ojtaknej el Cham Jajawil, man ẍiok. Yujtol ayin wal caw Yajaw in chi walaꞌ tol masanil eb ok in ojtaknen elok, caxcꞌal unin, caxcꞌal icham anima.
A is ley Moisés txꞌoxbanilej yayji yuj juntzan tzet tzakan jayi, mantonak juntzan acaw tuꞌ. Yujtol a ley tuꞌ, cꞌam chi jeꞌ watxꞌnen oc eb chi yochej chi apni oc satak Dios yuj juntzan xajanbal chi akꞌlay junjun abil tuꞌ.
Caw wal ayxa is may ta chon aycꞌay yul kꞌab Cham Dios iquis.
A José, yanak oc Dios yin cꞌul. Yuj tuꞌ xan a yet toxa chi cami, max yaloncanok tol tꞌinan ok el eb israel bay Egipto. Max yalon cꞌapax canok, tzet yowalil ok yut eb is bakil.
Yel toni, a yet chi alay oc co yailal tuꞌ, cꞌam junok on chon tzaloj yuj co yailal tuꞌ yin aymanil, palta ta chi watxꞌji oc co nabal yuj, cꞌojancꞌulal chon jichloj oc yuj, cax chi jay co juncꞌulal.
Axca ton tuꞌ max yut yaben Jesús yail, yet max cam tiel conob, yet watxꞌ a is chiqꞌuil chi ion el yobtakil anima.
Chon yi aj wan Cham yuninalok, yin yakꞌbalnen is kꞌanej tol caw wal yel, yujtol axca tuꞌ max el yin cꞌul max on yutej, yet watxꞌ aj babel on satak masanil tzet yetal max yesnej ajok.
Co naek xin, tol max yaoc Abraham is cꞌul yin Dios, yuj tuꞌ xan max jeꞌ yiken tzet max akꞌlay yunej. Ato wal yet max yun cham jun tuꞌ, max txeclojcan el sicꞌlibil tol ay ton wal oc Dios yin cꞌul.
Ocanek yin cuscꞌulal, jichchajokab e cꞌul e yokꞌ sicꞌlibil. Meltzojokab oc e tzeꞌ yin okꞌil. Meltzojokabcan oc e tzalojcꞌulal yin cuscꞌulalil.
Jalek watxꞌ kꞌanej bay Dios, is Mam Cham Jajawil Jesucristo, yujtol max okꞌ cꞌul Cham jin. Max con yakꞌ aljok Cham yet cayelal, yuj yictzojbail Jesucristo xol eb camnak. Yuj tu xan chi jaoc yipok co cꞌul, tol aꞌ ok akꞌon co kꞌinal.
Caw miman yelapnok Cristo yul co sat, mac on txel chi jaoc co cꞌul yin, palta ay pax eb cꞌam chi yaoc cꞌul yin Cham. A ton yin juntzan tiꞌ chi yal txꞌan Un Tzꞌibbilcan axca tiꞌ:
yujtol tix wal yalon yul txꞌan Un tiꞌ:
A ayon tojol co nabal tiꞌ, puralxacꞌal ok on colchajok. Ta caytuꞌ ok yun co colchaj el ayon tiꞌ, ¿akxam wal eb cꞌam yelapnok Dios yul sat, cꞌal eb ajmul?
Yujtol a Cham Jajawil Jesucristo max akꞌon nachaj el wuj, tol manxa mimanok tiempo ayin ecꞌok.
Yuj tuꞌ, yowalil che natek juntzan tzet tzꞌibbilcan yuj eb chekbej Dios yet payxa, eb is chekbej sicꞌbil el yuj. Naek cꞌapaxtek chekbanil Cham Jajawil co Colomal. A is chekbanil tuꞌ, albilxacan ayex juj ayon is chekbej on tiꞌ.
Ta chi jikej tzet chi al-lay xin, wal yel ay ton wal co camcꞌulal yin Cham sicꞌlibil. Axca ton tiꞌ chi yun jojtaknen elok, tol ayon ton oc yin Cham.
Yuj tu xin, ta yel wali ayon oc yin Cham, manchakxa co beybalnej yobtakil. Palta tzancꞌal mac acꞌalaꞌ beybalnen yobtakil xin, cꞌam chi yaoc nabal yin Cham, cax manto ojtakbilok Cham yuj.
Yuj Cham Yespíritu max cajbaj oc jin, xan jojtak tol ayon ton oc yin Cham, cax ay cꞌapax oc Cham jin junjun on.
Yakꞌokabcꞌal co Mam Dios, yetok Cham Jajawil Jesucristo is watxꞌcꞌulal ayex. Okꞌokab cꞌul eb e yin, yakꞌokab cꞌapax eb is juncꞌulal ayex bay tuꞌ, yujtol ayoc co nabal yin tzet yetal tol yel, cax ay pax co camcꞌulal.
Yetok cꞌapaxok, naektek tzet yayji juntzan eb ángel, eb maj mayjok yin yopiso, palta tol max bekcan eb is cajlobal. A tinaniꞌ, cꞌanani pixay eb yetok cadena yin tojbalkꞌinal. Preso yayji eb xol kꞌekkꞌinal yuj Dios, masantacꞌal ok jay jun cꞌual caw wal miman yelapnok, catatuꞌ ok beycꞌulnelay eb.
A nan xol juntzan batxlubal tuꞌ, ay jun mac lajan wal yili axca anima. Ayoc jun jokan pichilej yuj, chita ayol xol yakan. Ayoc jun miman sat cincho oro yin txam is cꞌul.
Palta a ex aj Tiatira, ex tol cꞌam che yaoc e nabal yin is cuybej ix ix tuꞌ, jun cuybej chi yal eb tol cuybej Satanás yaꞌ nachaj elok, cꞌam junokxa chekbanilej chi waltok ayex.
A is cawilal tuꞌ, a tuꞌ oyan oc 24 ẍila. A tuꞌ chotan ay 24 icham winak max wilaꞌ. Caw sak is pichil eb. Ayaj junjun is corona oro eb yin is jolom.
Cax max wilon nicꞌon el Cham chi yik Calnel tuꞌ jun babel sello. Max lajwi tuꞌ, max waben yalon junok eb querubín tuꞌ, axca wal nilili bil cꞌu, caytuꞌ yoc yul nukꞌ, yet max yalon axca tiꞌ: Sebach, ẍi.
Max lajwi tuꞌ, max kꞌanlen jun eb icham winak ayin axca tiꞌ: ¿Mactxel eb sak pichil tiꞌ cha naꞌ? ¿Baytal tax titnak eb cha naꞌ? ẍi ayin.
—Xuyil eb canwan ángel pixan bay ti aꞌ miman Éufrates, ẍi bay.
A wal yet jun bek tuꞌ, ok ecꞌ jun quixcab. Caw ow ok yun yeqꞌui. Xiwil na ok aycꞌay bay jun miman conob tuꞌ. Yin lajlajon bulan ok yun yaycꞌay junjun bulan. Ukeb mil anima ok cam yuj. A pax juntzanokxa anima xin, caw ok xiw eb sicꞌlibil. Ok yalon eb tol caw miman yelapnok Dios ayicꞌ bay satcan.
Max yiay ba eb bay jun dragón tuꞌ, yujtol aꞌ max akꞌon yikbej jun chi yik Noꞌ tuꞌ, xan max yi cꞌapax ay ba eb bay jun chi yik Noꞌ tuꞌ. Max yalon eb axca tiꞌ: Tok ay junok chi apni axca jun chi yik Noꞌ tiꞌ. ¿Xin ta ay junok chi jeꞌ yakꞌlen owal yetok? ẍi eb.
Axa yeltek junxa ángel yul templo Dios. Max yalon yin ipejal bay jun chotan ay yiban asun tuꞌ axca tiꞌ: Poloc a polbal yin a wajon aj eb anima tol watxꞌxa yayji, yujtol tiempoxa wajlay aj eb, ẍitok bay.
A eb espíritu yob tuꞌ, max yakꞌ eb wajbaj oc ba eb mimek yajaw bay jun lugar chi yik Armagedón yin is tiꞌ hebreo.
Yuj max yiaj can ba sicꞌlibil, cax asan yin beyomal max yaoc is nabal, xan caytuꞌ che yut e yaon oc yailal cꞌal cuscꞌulal yin. Ilab tol max naꞌ axca tiꞌ: Ayin tiꞌ, reina in. Chotan in ay bay in despacho. Mayin lajanok axca junok ix ix camnakxa yichamil. Cꞌam bakꞌin ok wil yailal jabok, ẍi.
Max waben yoc jun kꞌanej chi eltek bay is despacho Dios tol max yal axca tiꞌ:
Max wilon cꞌapax yin masanil eb camnak, tol lecan oc eb masanil satak Dios, eb mimanbil cꞌal eb cꞌam yelapnok. Lajwi tuꞌ, max jaklay juntzan txꞌan libro, cax ay junxa txꞌan max jaklay cꞌapaxtok, a ton txꞌan libro yet kꞌinalej tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal, cax max beycꞌulnelay tzetak yetal max el yunen junjun eb camnak tuꞌ, atacꞌalaꞌ tzet tzꞌibbil ay yul juntzan libro tuꞌ.
Cꞌam junok yobtakil ok uj yul jun conob tuꞌ. Cꞌam junok mac chi unen tzet yajbejtak yuj Dios ok oc bay tuꞌ. Cꞌal mac lekꞌtiꞌ, tutun wal cꞌam junok ok oc bay tuꞌ. Asannej eb tzꞌibbil ay is bi yul txꞌan libro yet kꞌinalej tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal, asan eb ok ocok. A txꞌan libro tuꞌ, yet Cham chi yik Calnel.
